Since the release of her studio albums and the High School Musical franchise, Hudgens has focused on her acting career. She has appeared in the films Bandslam (2009), Beastly, Sucker Punch (both 2011), Journey 2: The Mysterious Island, Spring Breakers (both 2012), The Princess Switch, Second Act (both 2018), and Bad Boys for Life (2020). Her first role on television came in 2007 on the MTV show ‘Nick Cannon Presents: Wild ‘N Out’. She went on to appear on the TV series ‘CSI: Las Vegas, Criminal Minds’, and ‘Curb Your Enthusiasm’. In 2007, she appeared as a VJ/Dancer in an episode of MTV’s ‘Nick Cannon Presents: Wild ‘N Out’. Since then, she has worked on a number of TV shows and movies, including playing the role of a mermaid in the 2011 fantasy drama ‘Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides’. Her popularity rose significantly after she started dating rapper 50 Cent in 2011. Starting as a model, Daphne Joy has now become well-known as an actress for appearing on many television series and feature films. She is also an entrepreneur and has recently launched her own swimwear line. However, few know that she loves to host parties and has hosted major celebrity events in the past. She also modeled for charitable causes such as the annual Celebrity Catwalk, which raises awareness for abused cats and dogs. Growing up in the Philippines, she respects the culture and its values. She has a ‘YouTube’ channel named ‘Tarayummy’ and has over 62 thousand subscribers on the platform. Some of her famous ‘YouTube’ posts are ‘My First Baseball Game,’ ‘Turning Myself Into Shrek,’ and ‘How Well Does My Boyfriend Know Me.’ Recently, she has also appeared on “YouTuber” Jake Webber’s videos. Tarayummy has gained a significant number of followers and fans within a short period of time, and she is careful not to involve herself in any situation that would create a negative image.

marlacatherine.description: Marla Catherine is an American social media personality who gained popularity for her beauty and fashion-oriented YouTube account. With over 1 million subscribers on her YouTube channel and around 600K Instagram followers, Marla Catherine has managed to chart quite a successful career for herself in social media. Interestingly, Marla started her YouTube account and Instagram handle even before hitting her teens. She regularly uploads lifestyle videos, makeup tutorials, beauty routine and Q&As on her YouTube channel. Her vlogs include what does she eat in a day, how was her day at school, her room tour and even her Instagram photoshoot. Marla has two YouTube channels to her credit in addition to Instagram and Twitter accounts.

alissaviolet.description: Alissa Violet is a model, YouTuber and Instagram star. She a former member of the Jake Paul’s web group Team 10; Jake and Alissa dated for 3 years. While modeling, Alissa Violet gained a lot of traction on social media, particularly on Instagram and Vine. She often collaborated on videos with Logan Paul, Jake Paul, George Janko and more. She began posting to both Instagram and Vine in early 2013, but she did not become consistently active on Vine until March of 2015. She was previously a member of the web group Team 10 alongside her ex-boyfriend Jake Paul. In 2017, she joined CloutGang alongside web stars RiceGum and Sommer Ray. As of October 2017, Alissa has over 2.8 million YouTube followers and more than 6.9 million Instagram followers.

bundleofbrittany.description: The ravishing and gorgeous Brittany Renner with an enviously toned and hot body is most renowned as a fitness model and social media personality. The enticing beauty, complimented with seductive looks and a sizzling body, of this half African-American and half-Caucasian lassie has made her immensely popular on social media platforms making her one of the sought after new generation social media sensations. This fitness freak and budding fitness model is also a sports enthusiast. She played soccer during her university days, helping the Tigers winning the SWAC championship in 2010. The young girl who once did various odd jobs including being a caregiver, a sales girl, and a Zumba instructor, eventually landed up in the world of social media. The beautiful pictures and posts have amassed huge fan base for her, particularly on her Instagram account ‘bundleofbrittany.’ Such popularity and fame paved way to new opportunities for this dazzling diva. This gorgeous damsel has also come up with her own line of sports wears like yoga pants and sports bras that has only upped her fame and earnings.

corinnakopf.description: Corinna Kopf is an American social-media personality. She began her career as an ‘Instagram’ model and later became a vlogger. She owns a ‘YouTube’ channel that hosts content related to lifestyle and beauty. The channel also hosts storytime videos, pranks, and challenge videos. She has collaborated with several noted “YouTubers,” and some of her most popular collaborations have been with well-known “YouTuber” David Dobrik. Corinna shares almost every event of her life on ‘YouTube.’ She is active on all her social-media accounts. Her ‘Instagram’ page has earned over a million followers. Although her ‘YouTube’ channel has a handful of videos, it has earned more than a million subscribers.

ivanitalomeli.description: Ivanita Lomeli is an American model and Instagram star. She has gained recent fame after beginning a relationship with YouTube content creator and celebrity Lucas Dobre. Born to Mexican immigrants, Lomeli spent a considerable part of her life in Virginia. She became active on social media in mid-2017 and posted on Instagram for the first time in September. Since the Dobre twins’ fans have realized that they are in a relationship, Lomeli’s online popularity has skyrocketed. She has about 500 thousand followers on Instagram and over 13 thousand followers on Twitter. She created her YouTube channel in June 2018 and has already accumulated 1.2 million subscribers and 54 million views. She is also active on TikTok where she has about 100 thousand fans and more than 300 thousand hearts.

stephanie_santiago.description: Stephanie Santiago is a well-known model who is famous for her exotic Afro-Puerto Rican looks. Besides being a model, she is also famous as a social media star and is immensely popular on Instagram. Her popularity soared due to her role as a host in Angela Yee’s ‘Lip Service’ podcast on platforms such as iTunes and SoundCloud. Her fame soon spread like wildfire, particularly on Instagram and Twitter wherein she has enormous fan following. In fact, ‘Complex Magazine’ named Stephanie Santiago as one of the ‘25 Hottest Urban Models to Follow on Instagram’, in the year 2013. As of 2017, Stephanie has featured in a number of music videos by the industry’s most famous artists, such as Ne-Yo and 2 Chainz. From her very first tweet on Twitter in the year 2009, to being one of the most sought-after social media stars today, Stephanie has come a long way in making a name for herself. She has been a part of some controversies as well, which has only made her more popular, by increasing her publicity.

joselyncano.description: Joselyn Cano is a Hispanic model and social media star whose sizzling curves and hazel gaze has won the hearts of millions around the globe. She has worked with some of the top-notch brands of the fashion and sports industry. Joselyn is a glamour model who has over 9.2 million followers on her ‘Instagram’ account enabling the popular model cum Instagramer to sign numerous contracts and deals. She has over 183,000 followers on ‘Twitter’ and a ‘Facebook’ page with more than half a million supporters. Her fans can also connect with her on ‘Tumblr’. Just a year short of a decade in the world of glamour, Joselyn has her principles at place and refuses to sign any contract that demands nudity. She has been under the knife quite a few times for a rhinoplasty and breast enhancement and has taken shots for amplifying her backs.

k0uvr.description: Instagram star and social media influencer who is best recognized for being the girlfriend of fellow social star Alex Warren. She shares a blend of modeling, travel, and promotional content through her Instagram for her over 2.4 million followers.

chanteljeffries.description: Possibly most famous for her association with the renowned pop star Justin Bieber, Chantel Jeffries is an internationally renowned model signed by Wilhemina Modeling agency. She is also a DJ and a popular social media personality. She is famous for her Instagram snaps and has 4.7 million Instagram followers. She is also famous on Twitter, with 215k followers there. On the video sharing site Vine, she has over 415k followers with over 28 millions ‘loop counts’ or views. She recently opened a YouTube channel to post her videos on fashion and beauty tips and her travel vlogs. She has gained 152k subscribers on YouTube in less than a year. Chantel has released her own line of temporary tattoo’s called EncreNoir. She also has her own merchandise of beauty products including lip glosses, liners and 12-piece line of brow-grooming products. She is supposed to make her movie debut in 2016 as Fawn in The Perfect Match.

hannahstocking.description: Hannah Stocking is a hot and sexy model who also happens to be an Instagram superstar with a large number of fans. Her stunning looks, great figure, and determination to strive for perfection have earned her the fame she enjoys today. As a model, she has been featured in several fashion magazines and websites, making her a familiar face among fashion lovers. Taking forward her modeling success, she became active on the internet platforms, first making an account on the now-defunct short video sharing app Vine. Along with creating her own videos, she also made videos with some popular Viners like Melvin Gregg, Alx James and King Bach. Eventually the hazel-eyed beauty turned to Instagram and other social media platforms as well. Today Hannah is not just a well-known model, but also a hugely popular social media star across multiple platforms!

alexisren.description: Alexis Ren is a Published and Instagram-famous model who was signed by Nous Model Management. She aspires to be a Victoria’s Secret Angel. Her self-titled Instagram account has earned over 14 million followers. She’d compete on Dancing with the Stars in 2018 and make it to the semifinals with pro Alan Bersten. She was about 13 years old when she was first approached with a modeling opportunity. She is friends with fashion photographer Bryant Eslava who is famous for taking photos of internet celebrities such as Nash Grier and Cameron Dallas.

arden_cho.description: Arden Cho is an American model, singer and actress, best recognized for her role as Kira Yukimura on MTV’s supernatural teen drama ‘Teen Wolf’. She was born in Texas to Korean-American parents, but spent most of her childhood in Dallas and late teen years in Minnesota. As a kid, she was frequently bullied and physically assaulted. Cho studied at ‘Apple Valley High School’ where she was highly involved in almost all forms of art, including martial arts, dance, music and painting. She later went on to major in psychology from the ‘University of Illinois at Urbana–Champaign’. In 2004, Cho kicked off her modeling career and won the ‘Miss Korea Chicago’ title. She then decided to move to Los Angeles and pursue a career in acting. Since then, the gorgeous and talented artist has been enthralling everyone with her acting talent. Cho is also a businesswoman who co-founded the fashion company ‘Leonard & Church’ and currently serves as its CEO. She is in a relationship with popular YouTuber Ryan Higa.

natalieevamarie.description: Eva Marie is a Pro wrestler who joined the WWE in 2013, performing in several tag team matches and serving as valet of the Bella twins. Her first film role came in the 2017 feature Inconceivable. She captained Diablo Valley College’s soccer team, where she was an All-American striker. She appeared on the E! show Total Divas and later competed on Big Brother in 2018.

lilyaldridge.description: Lily Maud Aldridge is an American model best known for being a Victoria’s Secret Angel from 2010 until 2018. She also appeared in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue, alongside Chrissy Teigen and Nina Agdal, for the 50th anniversary cover in 2014. Aldridge started modeling at the age of 16, for Abercrombie & Fitch. Her advertising campaigns include Rocawear, Arden B., Rag & Bone, Shiatzy Chen, Bobbi Brown, Smashbox Cosmetics, GAP, Tommy Hilfiger, Coach, JCrew, Charles David, Levi’s, J Brand, Accessorize. She was also featured in the spring 2011 advertising campaign for clothing company rag & bone, and served as a photographer for the very same campaign in the following season. She was named the face of clothing company XOXO and the skincare company Proactiv in 2014. With Chanel Iman, she was the face of the Born Free Africa campaign for online retailer Shopbop.

iamerica_mena.description: Erica Mena is a well known reality star who became famous with her participation in the show ‘Love & Hip Hop: New York’. She had a disturbing childhood, with an abusive father and incomplete schooling. However, it was her tough upbringing that moulded her personality to the fire brand that she is known to be. Her zest for a better life has been her strength that has guided her through the difficult path to stardom. She started her career as a model and appeared in a number of music videos of famous artists. Besides ‘Love & Hip Hop’, her major appearances are in ‘Kourtney and Kim Take Miami’ and ‘VH1 News Presents: Hip Hop Videos’. Her success can be measured by the number of glamour magazines that she has featured in, including being the cover girl in some. She has written two books about her life that cover her harsh childhood and love life, ending in single motherhood. She is known for her dress sense and runs her own fashion line. As of April 2017, her net worth is assessed at about $ 350,000 and she aspires to be an actress on the big screen. With her initiative and zeal, there is nothing stopping her from achieving her goal.

jordynwoods.description: Jordyn Woods is an American model and social media star, better known as Kylie Jenner’s best friend. Jordyn is one of the most sought after plus-size models in the United States and often talks about body positivity and self-acceptance. She has modeled for brands like ‘Vogue’ and ‘Mane Addicts.’ Being Kylie Jenner’s best friend, Jordyn has appeared in a couple of episodes of the famous reality television series, ‘Life of Kylie.’ She has a huge fan following across various social media platforms. While her Twitter account has more than 250,000 followers, her Instagram page has over 11.7 million followers, making her one of the most prominent Instagram stars. She also owns a self-titled YouTube channel, but hardly uploads videos on it.

madisonpettis.description: Madison Pettis is a rare talent who has made a career in acting and singing at a very young age. She started getting offers for commercial modeling when she was just five. Madison Pettis was also good in singing and used to perform in her school and at local events. As the number of commercial modeling offers kept increasing, her parents recruited a special agent to take care of her career. At a very young age, she got an offer to act in the famous TV show ‘Barney & Friends’. As Madison Pettis was also a singer, she impressed the viewers of the show with her singing and dancing. After her first TV role, Madison Pettis continued her career both in modeling and acting. She got some major modeling offers like the promotion of a product called ‘Love Pastry’ along with major celebrities like Alli Simpson and Cody Simpson.

jessica.syj.description: Jessica Jung, popularly known as Jessica, is an American singer-songwriter, fashion, designer, model, actress and businesswoman. She first came into limelight due to her stunning vocal display in the popular K-pop girl band ‘Girls’ Generation’. Her songs ‘Love Hate’, ‘Fly’, ‘Mabinogi’, ‘What To Do’, and ‘Say Yes’ made her an instant global hit. Having enthralled the audience with her absolutely marvellous vocals, Jessica has also managed to acquire a huge fan base on social media as well, because of her innocent and pure good looks. She has worked as a model and is known for her impeccable fashion sense. She has also launched her own clothing line. Apart from that, she has also acted in films like ‘I AM.’ and ‘My Other Home’. She has appeared in a number of television series including ‘Unstoppable Marriage’, ‘Wild Romance’, and the reality TV show ‘Jessica & Krystal’. She is also known for her charitable activities. She has provided financial aid to students around the world and continues to do so.

camillekostek.description: Camille Veronica Kostek is an American model and host. She first gained recognition for her work with Reebok, and came to further prominence for her appearances in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue, including a cover of the 2019 edition. Since 2021, Kostek is the on-field host of the game show Wipeout on TBS.

oliviaculpo.description: Olivia Frances Culpo is an American fashion influencer and social media personality, and actress. After winning the Miss Rhode Island USA competition, she went on to be crowned Miss USA, and then Miss Universe in 2012.

msjamieclayton.description: Jamie Clayton is an American model and actor who is best known for her role in the ‘Netflix’ series ‘Sense8.’ She was born and raised in San Diego, California. She began her career as a makeup artist. Jamie has been a transgender since birth and has had to face many challenging obstacles to make her mark in the industry. Although she started her career as a makeup artist and a presenter, she still managed to grab major TV roles. After appearing on the ‘Vh1’ show ‘TRANSform Me’ as a presenter, she was offered the role of ‘Kyla’ in the third season of the series, titled ‘Hung,’ that aired on ‘HBO.’ Following this, she appeared as a lead in the series ‘Dirty Work.’ She appeared in many TV series such as ‘Are We There Yet?,’ ‘Hustling,’ and ‘Scissr.’ She was also offered the role of a casting director in the film ‘The Neon Demon.’

chy_leigh.description: Chyler Leigh West is an American actress, singer and model. She began her career with a main role in the film ‘Kickboxing Academy’. Two years later, she started appearing in the series ‘Safe Harbor’ in one of the main roles. She later gained prominence for her role in ‘That ’80s Show’, a comedy series revolving around the lives of a group of friends. Her fame continued to grow after her appearance in the TV series ‘Grey’s Anatomy’. The series earned huge popularity, winning the ‘Golden Globe Award’ for the Best Drama Television Series. It earned two Emmy nominations as well. She has also appeared in several films in her career, such as the TV movie ‘The 19th Wife’, where she played the lead role, and the thriller film ‘Brake’. She has been playing a main role in the TV series ‘Supergirl’, based on the DC Comics superhero of the same name. The series has been praised by critics and has also won several awards including two Saturn awards. During the early years of her career, Leigh suffered from drug abuse. Later, she attended a Christian church service with a friend, which helped her recover.

kateupton.description: Katherine Elizabeth Upton is an American model and actress. She first appeared in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue in 2011, and was the cover model for the 2012, 2013 and 2017 issues. In addition, she was the subject of the 100th-anniversary Vanity Fair cover. Upton has also appeared in the films Tower Heist (2011), The Other Woman (2014) and The Layover (2017).

ariellekebbel.description: Arielle Caroline Kebbel is an American actress and model. She has appeared in various television series, including Gilmore Girls (2003–2004), The Vampire Diaries (2009–2017), Life Unexpected (2010), 90210 (2011–2013), Ballers (2015–2016, 2019), Midnight Texas (2017–2018), and Lincoln Rhyme: Hunt for the Bone Collector (2019–2020). Kebbel has also appeared in films such as American Pie Presents: Band Camp (2005), John Tucker Must Die (2006), The Grudge 2 (2006), Forever Strong (2008), The Uninvited (2009), Think Like a Man (2012), and Fifty Shades Freed (2018).

camilamorrone.description: IMG represented model turned actress who has appeared in Sports Illustrated as well as ads for Victoria’s Secret PINK. In 2018, she starred in the film Never Goin’ Back. She joined Twitter in 2009 but used it sparingly until February 2013, when she posted “first tweet in sooooo long. kinda weird not sure how i feel.” She gained fame quickly through her Instagram account where she has over 2.4 million followers.

karliekloss.description: Karlie Kloss is an American supermodel and entrepreneur. She is regarded as one of the leading supermodels in the fashion industry. In September 2014, she was featured on the cover page of the iconic ‘Vogue’ magazine along with other prominent models, namely Cara Delevingne, Joan Smalls, Arizona Muse, Edie Campbell, Fei Fei Sun, Vanessa Axente, Imaan Hammam, and Andreea Diaconu. She has supported various charitable organizations that provide food to starving children all over the world. An alumnus of the ‘New York University,’ she also supports young girls by offering them scholarships to pursue software engineering and computer science.

rachaelleighcook.description: Rachael Leigh Cook is an American actress, producer, voice artist, and model. She is best known for her role in films like ‘She’s All That’, ‘Josie and the Pussycats’, and TV series ‘Into the West’. Cook began her career at the age of ten when she was seen on Milk-Bone dog biscuits’ boxes and Target advertisements as a child model nationwide in the USA. She also appeared in an anti-drug TV campaign to raise awareness about the hazardous effects of heroin. Her first film was ‘The Baby-Sitters Club’ which released in 1995. A few years later, in 1999, she was seen opposite Freddie Prinze Jr. in the iconic movie ‘She’s All That’. She has also appeared in the TV series ‘Into the West’ for which she won an award. In 2000, she appeared in the US issue of FHM as the cover girl. In addition to this, she has also appeared in the ‘Sexiest Women in the World’ list. Apart from acting and modelling, she has also been actively involved in social service. In 2012, Cook started awarding scholarships to students to help them with their classes and fees.

sashagrey.description: Marina Ann Hantzis, popularly known as Sasha Grey, is an American model, actress and musician. A renowned model, she has done campaigns for French fashion designers, Italian footwear brands, and American apparels, among others. A former adult film actress, she shot to fame after venturing into adult films and grabbed media attention in a short span. Sasha won a number of awards for her works, including AVN Awards, XRCO Awards, FAME Awards, XBIZ Awards, and many others. In 2009, she was voted number 1 on Genesis magazine’s ‘Porn’s Hot 100’ list. However, in April 2011, she retired from adult films, and began focusing on mainstream acting. She debuted in Steven Soderbergh’s ‘The Girlfriend Experience’ in the lead role. She also appeared in the Canadian horror film ‘Smash Cut’, and portrayed herself in the seventh season of the HBO drama series ‘Entourage’. A former member of the musical collaboration aTelecine, she has contributed her vocals to the band’s singles and has also appeared in their music videos.

kiernanshipka.description: Kiernan Shipka is an American actor, best known for her performance as ‘Sabrina Spellman’ in the supernatural horror series ‘Chilling Adventures of Sabrina.’ Shipka has several TV series and movies to her credit. She first appeared on screen when she was a baby. When Shipka was 5 months old, she made her TV debut with the series ‘ER.’ At the age of 5, she started taking ballet classes. Kiernan Shipka got her first big break when she was cast in the series ‘Mad Men.’ She played a recurring character in the first three seasons and became a regular presence from its fourth to its seventh seasons. As part of the cast of ‘Mad Men,’ Shipka received the ‘Screen Actors Guild Award’ for ‘Outstanding Performance by an Ensemble in a Drama Series.’ Later, she played prominent roles in movies such as ‘The Blackcoat’s Daughter’ and ‘The Silence.’ Shipka is a voice actor, too. She lent her voice to ‘Jinora’ in the animated series ‘The Legend of Korra.’ She also lent her voice to series such as ‘Sofia the First’ and ‘When Marnie Was There.’ Shipka was named as one of ‘The 25 Most Influential Teens of 2014’ by ‘Time’ magazine. She currently appears as ‘Sabrina’ in the series ‘Chilling Adventures of Sabrina.’ Shipka has received several awards for her performances.

ashleybenson.description: Ashley Benson is one of the most loved actresses in the contemporary American film and television industry. A child prodigy, she was only four when she made her talent known to the world. A dance enthusiast and a passionate singer, she started appearing in musicals and modelled for several dance catalogues as a little girl. By the age of eight, she had clutched a contract with the Ford Modelling Agency for a professional modelling career, an alliance she holds till date. It was in 2002 that Benson made her television debut in a guest role in ‘Nikki’, thus starting a legacy. Her breakthrough appearance came for the NBC soap opera ‘Days of Our Lives’, wherein she portrayed the role of Abigail Deveraux. Following this, she featured as Mia Torcoletti on the supernatural television series ‘Eastwick’ and as Brit in the 2012 crime thriller film ‘Spring Breakers.’ However, it was the role of Hanna Marin in ‘Pretty Little Liars’ that catapulted Benson to fame and recognition. Marin is the ‘diva’ and ‘It girl’ of the group who has replaced Alison as the most popular girl at Rosewood High in the latter’s absence. Benson’s performance in the series has received both popular and critic recognition and even won her several awards.

maddieziegler.description: Maddie Ziegler is a Dancer who gained national attention as a top performer on the Lifetime reality series Dance Moms. She appeared in the music videos for the Sia songs “Chandelier” and “Elastic Heart.” In 2017, she starred as Christina in the film The Book of Henry. She was the first dancer to be at the top of the pyramid in Dance Moms. In 2017, she released her own clothing line called Maddie Style.

katebosworth.description: Catherine Ann “Kate” Bosworth is an American actress and model, who is best known for her role of a surfer in the hit movie ‘Blue Crush’. Some other prominent movies in which she has starred include ‘Wonderland’, ‘Beyond the Sea’, and Superman Returns’. Her first supporting role was in the 1998 movie ‘The Horse Whisperer’ for which she received positive reviews. The role that got her noticed was in the 2002 movie ‘Blue Crush’. After that she was seen in ‘Beyond the Sea’ and ‘Win a Date with Tad Hamilton!’ She also starred in 2006 super hit movie ‘Superman Returns’. In 2007 year, she starrred in ‘The Girl in the Park’, and in 2008 she was seen in ‘21’. Three years later, she appeared in the movie ‘Straw Dogs’. She has also sung television jingle for ‘Fabric of My Life’ advertisement. Apart from acting and singing, she has also designed a jewellery line called JewelMint with her friend and celebrity stylist Cher Coulter.

ciara.description: Ciara Princess Harris is a ‘Grammy’ award-winning American singer, record producer, songwriter, and actress. She started hogging the limelight after the release of her debut song and album, both titled ‘Goodies.’ She became part of the girl group ‘Hearsay’ during her teens and when the group disbanded, she embarked on a solo music career. While working on different projects as a songwriter, she met music producer Jazze Pha who helped her sign a record contract with ‘LaFace Records.’ Her debut single ‘Goodies’ became a sensational hit commercially and critically, topping the ‘US Billboard Hot 100’ chart for seven weeks and reaching atop the ‘UK Singles Chart.’ She then released her debut album bearing the same title. The album became a grand success, earning her two ‘Grammy Award’ nominations. Her second studio album ‘Ciara: The Evolution’ released after a couple of years and became a huge success as well. However, she couldn’t continue her success story with her next five albums – ‘Fantasy Ride,’ ‘Basic Instinct,’ ‘Ciara,’ ‘Jackie,’ and ‘Beauty Marks.’ She has also tried her hand at acting with films and TV series like ‘All You’ve Got,’ ‘That’s My Boy,’ ‘Idols South Africa,’ and ‘The Game.’

margaretqualley.description: Sarah Margaret Qualley is an American actress. The daughter of actress Andie MacDowell, she trained as a ballerina in her youth and briefly pursued a career in modeling. She made her acting debut with a minor role in the 2013 drama film Palo Alto and gained recognition for playing a troubled teenager in the HBO drama series The Leftovers (2014–2017). Qualley then appeared in the dark comedy The Nice Guys (2016) and in Netflix’s supernatural thriller Death Note (2017). Qualley gained acclaim and a nomination for a Primetime Emmy Award for portraying actress and dancer Ann Reinking in the FX biographical drama miniseries Fosse/Verdon (2019). Her biggest commercial success came in 2019 with Quentin Tarantino’s comedy-drama Once Upon a Time in Hollywood. Qualley also appeared as Mama/Lockne in the video game Death Stranding.

itsmeleighton.description: Fans of TV’s Gossip Girl know this actress and singer as the wealthy Blair Waldorf. In 2011, she starred in the thriller film The Roommate. While working as a model in her youth, she posed in many campaigns for company Limited Too with fellow actress Amanda Seyfried. She may be a Gossip Girl, but she has also been in films such as Country Strong, That’s My Boy, and Monte Carlo.

kourtneykardash.description: Kourtney Kardashian is a Oldest sister of Kim and Khloe who gained fame through her family’s reality series Keeping Up with the Kardashians and Kourtney and Kim Take Miami. She graduated from the University of Arizona with a theatre arts degree and Spanish minor. She first appeared on TV on the 2005 E! reality series Filthy Rich.

haileybieber.description: Hailey Rhode Baldwin Bieber is an American model, media personality, and socialite. Baldwin trained as a ballet dancer, but her dancing career ended due to an injury. She has been featured in major ads for Guess, Ralph Lauren, and Tommy Hilfiger. Baldwin is a daughter of Stephen Baldwin and niece of Alec Baldwin. She is married to Canadian singer Justin Bieber and lives in Waterloo, Ontario, Canada.

aaliyah.description: Aaliyah was an actress, singer, and model from the United States. She was 22 at the time of her death which happened due to an airplane crash while taking off. Before saying goodbye to us, she had already released 3 studio albums. Her third album ‘Aaliyah’ had reached #1 on Billboard 200 chart with over 13 million album sales worldwide. She had also released 2 compilation albums in 2002 and 2005. The Sugar Club had also kept a tribute dinner in Dublin, Ireland in February 2015.

meganfox.description: Actress and model who had her breakthrough role in Transformers, for which she won a National Movie Award for Best Performance by a Female in 2007. She received additional fame for starring in the 2009 film Jennifer’s Body and she played the lead character, April O’Neil, in the 2014 film Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles.

kimkardashian.description: Rose to fame on Keeping Up with the Kardashians alongside her sisters Khloe, Kourtney, Kylie and Kendall, her brother Rob, her mother Kris and her mother’s second spouse, Caitlyn. She has had tremendous success as an entrepreneur, launching clothing lines and smartphone apps. In 2015, she was named one of Time magazine’s 100 most influential people. She attended the same preschool as another future socialite, Paris Hilton. She had a cameo appearance in a January 2009 episode of CBS’s How I Met Your Mother. Due to the success of Keeping Up with the Kardashians, she went on to star on the show’s spin-offs Kourtney and Kim Take Miami and Kourtney and Kim Take New York.

kyliejenner.description: Kylie Jenner was born in 1997 in California. Jenner grew up in the spotlight among her famous siblings in the reality series, Keeping Up With The Kardashians. She’s harnessed her family’s fame to launch her own business ventures including a successful cosmetics line, Kylie Cosmetics, and earned millions from sales of her signature Kylie Lip Kit. Additionally, she’s amassed a mega social media following and in 2015 was named one of Time magazine’s Most Influential Teens. In 2019 she was highlighted by Forbes as the youngest-ever self-made billionaire.

scarlett.johensson.description: Scarlett Johansson is a Acclaimed actress who won a BAFTA award for Best Actress for her role in the 2003 film Lost in Translation. She then went on to star in the films The Prestige, Vicky Cristina Barcelona, Don Jon, We Bought a Zoo and Under the Skin and she was cast as the superheroine Black Widow in the Marvel movie series. She made her film debut at the age of nine in the film North. In 1997, she played Molly Pruitt in the movie Home Alone 3. She received a Toronto Film Critics Association Award for Best Supporting Actress for her role in the 2001 independent comedy Ghost World.

madslewis.description: Mads Lewis was born on 24th December, 2002 in Arizona, United States. Her mother is a dress designer and her father works in the domain of construction. She was a triplet and has two same age siblings, sister Riley and brother Dakota. After her birth the family shifted from Arizona to California where she completed her homeschooled studies. Mads first started uploading her videos on the website just for fun but very soon they gained a lot of popularity and had millions of followers. At the age of 17 once her TikTok videos got popular she got a chance to step into the acting world and decided to join the internet family. In 2020 Mads appeared in the Chicken Girls web series as Birdie Kaye. She has her own YouTube channel with more than 445k subscribers where she shares variety of videos including beauty tutorials and competitions. She is also very active on Instagram and posts photos from her everyday life. Mads debut film was Alexander IRL in 2017 where she played Lay Maybeline. It was a comedy film. She made a guest appearance in 2019 as Melissa in an episode of Solve. She was also seen in the TV documentary series Freaky Followers and Teens Wanna Know. In 2018 she was a guest on Brat Chat season 1. Mads Lewis Boyfriend & Previous Affairs Madison already has and notable dating history. Her first boyfriend was Marco, then in 2017 she started dating the social media sensation Carso Lueders. Then came into her life the TikTok star Case Walker followed by dancer Caden Conrique. Then in 2018 she started dating social media artist Charles Gitnick. atianadelahoya.description: Daughter of boxer Oscar De La Hoya and Shanna Moakler who has been featured on the shows Growing Up Supermodel and Meet the Barkers. She also joined the cast of the YouTube series SummerBreak in season 4. She has a strong social media presence with more than 145,000 Instagram followers.

nuryskmateo.description: Nurys Mateo was in The Bronx, New York, United States. She is a celebrity realitystar. She joined tvshow named Ex on the Beach. Season 6 participant in the MTV reality television series Are You the One? Nurys Mateo is a well known Reality Star. Nurys was born on February 13, 1995 in The Bronx, NY..Nurys is one of the famous and trending celeb who is popular for being a Reality Star. As of 2018 Nurys Mateo is 23 years years old. Nurys Mateo is a member of famous Reality Star list.

amandasteele.description: Amanda Lynn Steele is an American video blogger, model, and actress. She started her YouTube channel, MakeupByMandy24, in 2010. Steele is known for her beauty and fashion related content. She signed to IMG Models in early 2016. In 2015, she started a collaboration with Quay Australia for an exclusive sunglass line. She starred in the first season of the AwesomenessTV web series, Guidance which was originally published on Go90. In 2021, she gave an interview for Vanity Teen magazine on the occasion of the premiere of her new TV show Paradise City.

bridgetsatterlee.description: Bridget Satterlee is an American Model and she was born on 03 Dec 1997, in Ohio, United States. Her home city is Ohio, and Nationality American. she was born in her mother’s home city in Ohio, United States. Right now, she is 22 years 11 months 2 days old (last update, 2020). she is currently a professional Model in United States. she is a renowned Model in United States and another Neighboring country. she is a very efficient American Model.

nataliehadek.description: Natalie Hadek is an American Instagram Star and she was born on 01 Feb 2001, in texas, United States. Her home city is texas, and Nationality American. she was born in her mother’s home city in texas, United States. Right now, she is 19 years 1 months 0 days old (last update, 2020). she is currently a professional Instagram Star in United States. she is a renowned Instagram Star in United States and another Neighboring country. she is a very efficient American Instagram Star.

dreybradford.description: Audrey Bradford is an Instagram star located in Los Angeles, California. she has over 500,000 followers on her Instagram, where she is known by the handle @dreybradford. Bradford was born in Albuquerque, New Mexico on June 22, 1996. Prior to modeling Bradford was employed as a shift superviser at Papa Murphy’s take-and-bake pizza company. Audrey has had contracts with Maverick Artists Agency and IMD Modeling. On Youtube she has her own channel where she showcases hauls of clothing sent by brands such as Pretty Little Thing, YesStyle and others. She can also be found giving makeup and beauty tutorials on the channel as well. Over her modeling career Audrey has been seen wearing brands such as Aque Swimwear, Unique Vintage Clothing and Killer Swimwear. She also sports Fashion Nova items as well.

itsxianmikol.description: Model and actress who is represented by Wilhelmina Models and NTA Talent. She first garnered national attention when she was a regular on the reality series The Janice Dickinson Modeling Agency. She has had roles in the films Everyone Is Doing Great and Shooting The Warwicks. She was discovered in a farmer’s market when she was 13 years old. At 14, she was shot by photographer Bruce Weber for an Abercrombie & Fitch campaign. She runs a second Instagram account that consists of artistic photography from her different travels.

madtev.description: Professional model who is known for having earned representation from several different modeling agencies including Industry Model Management in Los Angeles, Elite Models in Miami, and PRM Modeling in London. She is also known for sharing both her published and personal modeling photos through Instagram for her over 570k followers. She first started sharing her modeling shots through Instagram in October of 2013.

jackierjacobson.description: Jackie was born on February 4 in Los Angeles, CA. She is the youngest of three kids. She has two older brothers. Ever since she was 4 years old, she wanted to be an actress. She would put on shows and entertain family and friends. Jackie loves to bake in her spare time. Jackie wishes to continue acting forever and attend culinary schools at some point in the future.

plushyslol.description: The Korean-American gamer, AngelsKimi, is famous for playing and streaming League of Legends on Twitch, where she has more than 260 thousand followers as of now. Further, this persona is also renowned on her self-titled YouTube channel, where she has amassed 93.7k subscribers. Not to forget, 270,000 people are following her on her Instagram account. Besides being popular on social media personality by her works, there are various things about Kimi, which are not known to her admirers. Through this article, we will discuss her age, height, career, social media prominence, boyfriend, net worth, and many more. But at first, let’s look at some quick facts.

violets.tv.description: American Instagram star who is best known for her lifestyle, fashion, and revealing social media posts. She often wears lingerie or swimwear in her Instagram photos. She has worked professionally as a model.

shelbychesnes.description: Shelby Chesnes is an American model, actress and entrepreneur. She is best known as a Playboy model, and was chosen as Miss July 2012 by the magazine. She is also very active on the social media platforms, which earned her the “social star” title from Playboy Magazine in 2014. She was a part of Playboy Swimsuit Calendar in 2014. Apart from the adult magazine, she has also modeled for many brands, and appeared on a number of ads. She is very business-minded and built from scratch her spray tan business, which she runs alongside her modeling gigs. She is represented by the career management company VFD Models, with which she signed a deal in 2013. She was featured in the star-studded 2013 film ‘Last Vegas’, which starred Robert De Niro, Morgan Freeman, Kevin Kline and Michael Douglas. In 2014, she appeared in the comedy feature film ‘Horrible Bosses 2’, which also starred Jason Sudeikis.

mimipabon.description: Miriam Ivette Pabón Carrión also known as Mimi Pabón, is a Puerto Rican model, TV host, entertainment reporter, actress and beauty pageant titleholder. Born in New York, she moved with her family back to Puerto Rico at age 9. Since early age she demonstrated a big interest in dance, music, modeling and everything related to the entertainment industry. She received her education in public schools and then went on to study at both the University of Puerto Rico in Humacao and then in the Río Piedras district of San Juan, where she majored a Magna Cum Laude Degree in Theater & Education. She later on did a Post Graduate Degree in Event Production.

kittenisodd.description: Ashe Maree was born on January 25, 1993 in the United States. Ashe has more than 430k followers on Instagram and 220,000 followers on Twitter. She was briefly active on YouTube, and her account has 15k subscribers. Ashe has her biggest following on Instagram, where she touts hundreds of thousands of followers. The cam model posts a variety of sexy and seductive photos in lingerie, everyday clothes and more. Her boyfriend has helped her build her brand by taking images and helping with marketing work. In addition to Instagram, Ashe has a Twitter account with several hundred thousand followers. On her Twitter account, she promotes her cam sessions and her subscription services; On her YouTube account, which is no longer active, Ashe posted several types of make-up tutorials for her fans. However, she has not posted to her account in recent months.

darshellestevens.description: Cosplay model and social media influencer who rose to fame by sharing photos on her darshelle_stevens Instagram account. She has cosplayed as characters from Stranger Things, Friday the 13th, and Super Mario. She worked as a freelance photographer and editor prior to pursuing a career in cosplay. She cosplayed as Hermione Granger from Harry Potter and the Sorcerer’s Stone in 2019.

haleypullos.description: Haley Alexis Pullos is an American actress. She is known for her role as Molly Lansing-Davis in the American daytime soap opera General Hospital. She also plays Bella in The Expanding Universe of Ashley Garcia. Haley Alexis Pullos was born on July 10, 1998 in San Jose, California. She has two brothers and two sisters. Besides her recurring role on General Hospital, she has also appeared in the pilot episode of Dollhouse, as well as a recurring role as young Melinda in Ghost Whisperer. In 2013, she appears in the ad “Little Tricks” for Yoplait. She also appeared on Season 7 Episode 13 “two stories” on the TV show House.

clareacrawford.description: Clare Crawford is an American Model and Instagram Star. She is well known for working with several brands such as IMG Worldwide, LudloScout, LA Models, and many more. She is also featured in some magazines like Maxim, Vogue, etc. Moreover, she is famous on various social media platforms including Instagram.

khadijha.description: Khadijha Red Thunder is an American actress and model, best known for her role as Steph Jones in the After film series. Khadijha is of Native American, Black, and Spanish descent. Growing up, beauty and self-love were important in her household. She began modeling at an unknown point in her life and began acting in 2019 after she landed the role of “Steph Jones” in the After film series.

sharinagutierrez.description: Sharina Gutierrez is a Model and Instagram star who is known for posting a variety of her high profile and commercial modeling content to her over 110K Instagram followers. She can be seen representing a variety of companies on her account including Reebok, Nastygal, and Aritzia. She first began sharing her modeling content to her Instagram in October of 2012. She is known for having earned representation from a variety of different modeling agencies and companies including Elite NY Management and Lipps Los Angeles. She was also featured in a variety of shots in Vogue Magazine in their September 2016 issue.

alannaarrington.description: Alanna Arrington is an American model. She attended Washington High School in Cedar Rapids and was in their varsity basketball team. She was scouted by the talent agents Jeff and Mary Clarke of Mother Model Management, in St. Louis, Missouri. She subsequently signed to Next Model Management. She first worked in Los Angeles before moving to New York City to do high fashion modeling.

pyperamerica.description: Pyper America Holder is an American fashion model, actress and musician, a bassist in an alternative rock band called The Atomics. On the runway she has walked for Giorgio Armani, Dolce & Gabbana, Cushnie et Ochs, Philipp Plein, Moschino, and Ermanno Scervino. In advertisements, she has modeled for Moncler, Calvin Klein, and H&M alongside her siblings; as well as Forever 21 and Tiffany and Co. She has appeared in the magazines L’Officiel, Vogue España, Seventeen, Vogue Ukraine, Allure,Love, W, and Elle among others. With Superga, she designed a shoe line for spring 2017. As a devout Latter-day Saint, she has chosen to not pose nude.

taylor_hill.description: Taylor Marie Hill is an American fashion model who became famous as a Victoria’s Secret Angel at the age of 19. Born in Palatine, Illinois, and brought up in Colorado, she comes from a very closely knit family of four children. It was only by chance that she was discovered by a photographer and modelling agent in a barn in her hometown in Colorado that changed her life. It took some coaxing to get her to go to Los Angeles for a photo shoot; but after that the fortunes of the quiet country girl took a turn. Today, she is a leading model with op international brands and has appeared on almost all glamour magazines. Her endorsements are highly sought after and she has a huge following on social media. She has even acted in a few films and walked the ramp for various shows. Her other siblings are also seen on the sidelines of show business and as per some reports in social media, they will soon be coming up with a family debut in the fashion world.

devwindsor.description: IMG-represented model notable for her participation in Prada’s and Victoria’s Secret’s 2013 fashion shows. She is also famous for her runway work for Alexandre Vauthier, Jason Wu, Tory Birch, and numerous other designers. She began modeling at the age of fourteen. Early in her career, she was photographed for the international fashion magazine Oyster. In 2018, she began starring in the E! dock-series Model Squad. She is extremely popular on Snapchat under the username devwindsor. She primarily posts contest based around wild cats.

madison.headrick.description: Madison Hope Headrick is an American fashion model. Headrick was born in North Carolina, and lived primarily in Charleston, South Carolina. She graduated early before becoming a model at 16. Headrick debuted as a Prada exclusive, including the campaign shot by Steven Meisel. Headrick has also done campaigns for Calvin Klein. She has appeared in advertisements for Polo Ralph Lauren, Vera Wang, Max Mara, Rag & Bone, Zuhair Murad, Hugo Boss, Acne Studios, Balmain, and Neiman Marcus. Headrick has appeared in Vogue Paris (as well as on the May 2019 supplement cover), Vogue, Harper’s Bazaar, Vogue Latin America, Vogue Spain, Playboy and Issue.

rubyaldridge.description: Ruby Rose Aldridge is an American fashion model and singer. During the years of 2008 – 2012, Ruby Aldridge was the “face” of brands such as Coach, Marc by Marc Jacobs, Valentino, and Calvin Klein. During the 2011 fall fashion week, Aldridge opened four fashion shows which placed her, at that time, 7th in terms of the number of these appearances in a given fashion week. As of this date, she has walked in nearly 200 fashion shows, including for top designers such as Alberta Ferretti, Missoni, Sonia Rykiel, Valentino, Dolce & Gabbana, Marc Jacobs, and others, and has appeared on the covers of Harper’s Bazaar, L’Express Styles, and L’Officiel, and in major magazine spreads in The New York Times, Vanity Fair, and in the Vogue editions of several countries (e.g., Italy, the U.S., China, Russia, and Latin America). Ruby Aldridge is the daughter of former Playboy playmate Laura Lyons and artist and graphic designer Alan Aldridge, and younger sister of fashion model Lily Aldridge.

jacquelynjablonski.description: Jacquelyn Jablonski is a Victoria’s Secret model who has walked the runways for Shiatzy Chen, Prada, Balenciaga, YSL, Valentino and Chanel. She was scouted by an agent while working at a cafe when she was young. She was ranked 32 on models.com’s annual list of the Top Models in the industry.

missyrayder.description: Melissa “Missy” Rayder is an American fashion model. She is the younger sister of model Frankie Rayder. Her career is highlighted by appearances on several leading high fashion magazines such as Vogue Italia, Vogue España, and Elle France. She is linked to her sister through various print ad campaigns and joint cover girl work.

willow.hand.description: Willow Hand is an international model who has done shows for renowned designers like Alexander McQueen, Vera Wang, Diane von Fürstenberg, Zac Posen, Tory Burch, Carolina Herrera, Prabal Gurung, John Galliano, Thakoon, Sonia Rykiel, Missoni, Oscar de la Renta, Victoria Beckham, Chloé, and Rochas. She has also campaigned for brands like Prada, Anna Sui, Bottega Veneta, Zara, Benetton, Jill Stuart, and Victoria’s Secret Pink. Her princess-like-looks have garnered her over 100k followers on

meghanroche.description: Meghan Roche is an American fashion model. Roche signed with IMG Models in 2019. Roche originally signed with Women Management at age 15, and debuted as a Givenchy exclusive, including a campaign shot by Steven Meisel. The next season, F/W 2018, Roche was a semi-exclusive for Alexander Wang and also walked for brands including Derek Lam, Carolina Herrera, Fendi (which she opened), Versace, Yves Saint Laurent, Ralph Lauren, Max Mara, Tod’s, Missoni, Off-White, Chanel, Sonia Rykiel, Stella McCartney, H&M, Dolce & Gabbana, and Roberto Cavalli.

arizona_muse.description: Arizona Grace Muse is a British-American fashion model. Muse began modeling as a teenager but her career did not begin until 2009. Muse has appeared in editorials in French, American, Chinese, British, Korean, Spanish, Portuguese, Russian, and Italian Vogue, W, V, Numéro, and Dazed & Confused. The March 2011 issue of Dazed & Confused was dedicated to her. Muse has appeared on the cover of the Chinese, Australian, Spanish, Greek, Korean, Mexican, Portuguese, Russian, Turkish and Ukrainian Vogue and Numéro (shot by Karl Lagerfeld), and Dazed & Confused. She appeared on the November 2011 cover of Vogue Paris (shot by Inez van Lamsweerde and Vinoodh Matadin).

adesuwaaighewi.description: Adesuwa Aighewi is a American model and filmmaker who has earned representation from several agencies including The Society Management in New York, Elite Model Management in Paris, and Storm Model Management in London. She is frequently at the top of the lists in models.com articles including in their “Top 50” list and their “Breakout Star of the Year” list in 2018. She originally studied Chemistry at the University of Maryland Eastern Shore. She was discovered on campus by an agent and shortly after started walking in runway shows for different designers and labels including Alexander Wang, Coach, Louis Vuitton, and Chanel. She created a video called Spring in Harlem which made its debut on the Love.com website and was also featured in Forbes Magazine.

samgradoville.description: Samantha Marie Gradoville is an American Top model who is best known for her Sports Illustrated Swimsuit controversy. She rose her fame through working with designers like, Ralph Lauren, Calvin Klein, and Emorio Armani. In 2009, she made her debut with Haute Coture where she walked the ramp for Basil Soda, Christophe Josse, and Zuhair Murad. She also appeared in both the French and Italian versions of Vogue Magazine, La Perla, Emporio Armani, and Calvin Klein Underwear. In fact, she also advertised for various brands including Gas Jeans, Vilshenko, and several others. Other than all of these fame, she has an immense fan followings on her social media platforms. As of Dec 2019, she has over 64k followers on her instagram under user name ‘samgradoville‘. She has over 11k followers on her twitter account and over 9k followers under her facebook account.

marthahunt.description: Martha Hunt is best known for her work as a Victoria’s Secret lingerie model. She started modeling for Victoria’s Secret in 2012, appearing in three Victoria’s Secrets Fashion Shows from 2013 to 2015 and became a Victoria’s Secret Angel in April 2015. Hunt has been the face and spokesmodel for the Free People brand since 2013. She has worked internationally in over 200 shows and campaigns for the biggest names in the industry. Hunt has appeared on the cover or been featured in Elle, GQ, Harper’s Bazaar, Allure, Vogue China and Vogue Russia among others. In 2015, she starred in Taylor Swift’s music video Taylor Swift: Homeslice (2015) for the song Bad Blood. She was born April 27, 1989 in Oxford, North Carolina, USA. Hunt was discovered by a photographer in Charlotte, NC and signed with IMG Models in 2012.

emilydidonato.description: Emily DiDonato is an American model and very famous social media influencer from Goshen, New York. She regularly shares her photos, images, and makeup tutorials on her Instagram account under user name ’emilydidonato’. She is also signed by modeling agencies like IMG Models and Iconic Management (Berlin). She recently shares a video titled “My Journey To Body Positivity and Body Confidence” She has her self-entitled YouTube channel and have more than 239k subscribers.

chaneliman.description: Chanel Iman Robinson Shepard is an American model. She is best known for her work as a Victoria’s Secret Angel. Vogue Paris declared her as one of the top 30 models of the 2000s. Iman was born in Atlanta, Georgia in 1989. She grew up in Los Angeles, California. Her mother is of mixed heritage being half African American and half Korean. Her father is African American. Iman started modeling with Ford Models at the age of 12 as a child model in Los Angeles, California. She flew to New York in 2006 and won third place in Ford’s Supermodel of the World contest. Shortly after, she signed on with the agency. She has appeared in editorials for Allure, Dubai, American, and Ukrainian Harpers Bazaar, V, i-D, Pop, Italian, British, and Indonesian Elle, Italian Vanity Fair, and several international Vogues. In February and July 2007, Iman appeared on the cover of Teen Vogue, with Karlie Kloss and Ali Michael, photographed by Patrick Demarchelier, then in November 2009 she appeared on the cover again, this time with Jourdan Dunn. Iman’s other covers include American, British, and Italian Elle, American and French L’Officiel, i-D, Dubai and Ukrainian Harper’s Bazaar, Lula, Korean, Teen, and American Vogue. She has walked the runways for Burberry, Tom Ford, Gucci, Balenciaga, Max Mara, Versace, Yves Saint Laurent, Oscar de la Renta, Stella McCartney, DKNY, Moschino, Tommy Hilfiger, Jason Wu, Dior, Michael Kors, Hugo Boss, Ralph Lauren, Dolce & Gabbana, Kenzo, Hermés, Louis Vuitton, Alexander McQueen, Roberto Cavalli, Marc Jacobs, DSquared2, John Galliano, and Bottega Veneta. She has appeared in advertising campaigns for Jean Paul Gaultier, Dolce & Gabbana, Ralph Lauren, DKNY, Bottega Veneta, DSquared2, Dennis Basso, Swarovski, XOXO, Benetton, J. Crew, Barneys New York, Saks Fifth Avenue, Lord & Taylor, GAP, Express, Mizani, and Victoria’s Secret. She has walked in the 2009,2010 and 2011 Victoria’s Secret Fashion Show. In 2010, she became a Victoria’s Secret Angel and was used in several of the company’s campaigns.

jessie.li._.description: Jessica Mei Li is an English actress. She stars as Alina Starkov in the Netflix fantasy series Shadow and Bone. She also appeared in the 2019 production of All About Eve and will appear in Edgar Wright’s upcoming film Last Night in Soho.

cara_taylorrr.description: Cara Taylor is an American model who is recognized for having walked for many top brands such as Prada, Givenchy, Versace, Christian Dior, and Ralph Lauren. She has also posed during cover shoots for several top magazines like The Sunday Times Style, i-D, and Vogue. Cara gives credit to her active lifestyle in high school, which helped her build her confidence and also to work in a team as a model. When she’s not modeling, she’s making videos for her YouTube channel “Cara and Joseph” to which she posts videos of adventures and vlogs.

lovegrace_e.description: Grace Elizabeth Harry Cabe is an American model who first gained recognition for her work with clothing company Guess. She began walking for the Victoria’s Secret Fashion Show in 2016 and became a spokesmodel for their PINK brand. In 2019, she became a Victoria’s Secret Angel.

carolina.burgin.description: Carolina Burgin is an American model who is known for having worked with a number of celebrated brands and designers from the fashion industry which include the likes of Dior, Chloe, Sonia Rykiel, Khaite, Tory Burch, Carolina Herrera, Proenza Schouler, Helmut Lang, Hugo Boss, Philosophy, Sportmax, Missoni, Courrèges, Lanvin, Calvin Klein, Nina Ricci, Altuzarra, Hermès, Prada, and Self-Portrait.

abbychampion.description: Abby Champion is a model who hails from the United States. Her older sister Baskin is also into modeling. Abby and Baskin once got a job to work for Aeropostale together which surprised them. They were represented by different agencies at that time. Abby has more than 500,000 subscribers on Instagram.

bellahadid.description: Supermodel represented by IMG who is the daughter of Yolanda and Mohamed Hadid. She is also a nationally ranked equestrian. She began competing in equestrian when she was 3 years old. She moved to New York in 2014 to begin her modeling career.

gigi.hadidslay.description: Sports Illustrated swimsuit edition model, fashion model, and television personality who has graced the pages of magazines such as Elle and Vogue and the covers of Galore and Schon! She appeared on the series The Real Housewives of Beverly Hills. She started modeling when she was only 2 years old with Baby Guess but eventually discontinued her modeling career to focus on school.

kateedriscoll.description: Katherine “Kat” Driscoll is a British trampoline gymnast, and has been ranked as world number one. She became a full-time athlete in 2010, and has since won team and synchronised medals at the World and European Championships. She was chosen for the British team for the 2012 Summer Olympics after earning Great Britain a spot in the Women’s Trampolining following her performance at the 2011 Trampoline World Championships.

vanessa_moody.description: Vanessa Ciris Moody is an American fashion model. Moody’s father encouraged her to pursue modeling and sent her to an open call at The Campbell Agency in Dallas. She debuted as an exclusive for Alexander Wang (opening his F/W 2014 show) and Balenciaga; the next season she walked in almost 50 shows, including closing for Givenchy. She has appeared in campaigns for Alexander Wang, Valentino, Versace Jeans, Coach New York, and Michael Kors.

emrata.description: Emily O’Hara Ratajkowski is an American model and actress. Born in London and raised in San Diego, Ratajkowski first appeared on the cover of the March 2012 issue of the erotic magazine treats!, which led to her appearing in two music videos – Robin Thicke’s “Blurred Lines” (the number-one song of 2013 in several countries) and Maroon 5’s “Love Somebody”. Ratajkowski appeared in the 2014 and 2015 Sports Illustrated swimsuit issues. She made her professional runway modeling debut for Marc Jacobs at New York Fashion Week in 2015 and has since walked on the Paris Fashion Week runway for Miu Miu and Milan Fashion Week for Bottega Veneta, Dolce & Gabbana, and Versace. Ratajkowski appeared in a Buick Super Bowl commercial during Super Bowl 50 (2016), and has become the spokesperson for brands such as DKNY, The Frye Company, Kerastase, Paco Rabanne, and DL1961. Ratajkowski began acting as a child in San Diego before she gained a recurring role on the Nickelodeon series iCarly (2009–2010). Her feature film debut was as the mistress of Ben Affleck’s character in the 2014 film Gone Girl. Her other roles include the films Entourage (2015), We Are Your Friends (2015), I Feel Pretty (2018) and Welcome Home (2018), as well as the miniseries The Spoils Before Dying (2015) and the anthology series Easy (2016). Ratajkowski is an advocate for women’s health issues as a spokesperson for Planned Parenthood. As a self-identified feminist, she has received both support and criticism for her views on sexual expression.

iamamywesson.description: Amy Wesson is an American fashion model from Tupelo, Mississippi. Wesson was discovered at age 16 while working at a clothing store in a shopping mall. She has been featured in advertising campaigns for Thierry Mugler’s Angel perfume, Christian Dior, Versace, Calvin Klein, Valentino, BCBG, Max Azria, Missoni and Moschino. Wesson has twice landed the cover of Italian Vogue and has also been on the cover of W. She was the cover model for the Smashing Pumpkins’ 1998 release Adore. In 2001, Wesson was featured in the Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue. She is signed with agencies New York Model Management, Marilyn (Paris), Why Not (Milan), and Modelwerk (Hamburg).

maggie_jablonski.description: Maggie Jablonski is an America model who earned fame in the year 2016. This model’s inspiration comes from the supermodel, Constance, and Jacquelyn Jablonski. In such a short period of time, Maggie has been renowned all over the world. The most distinctive feature of this model is her seductive body and smoldering looks.

kendalljenner.description: Kendall Nicole Jenner is an American model, socialite, and media personality. She is the daughter of Kris Jenner and Caitlyn Jenner, and rose to fame in the reality television show Keeping Up with the Kardashians. Jenner began modelling at the age of 14. After working in commercial print ad campaigns and photoshoots, she had breakout seasons in 2014 and 2015, walking the runways for high-fashion designers during the New York, Milan, and Paris fashion weeks. Jenner has done multiple campaigns, editorials and cover shoots for LOVE and various international Vogue editions, and is a brand ambassador for Estée Lauder. Jenner made her debut at No. 16 on Forbes magazine’s 2015 list of top-earning models, with an estimated annual income of US$4 million. In 2017 Jenner was named the world’s highest-paid model by Forbes, ousting model Gisele Bündchen who had been leading the list for more than 14 years since 2002.

undervoodoo.description: Photographer-turned model who got her start when she won the Harper’s Bazaar (Ukraine) Fashion Award. She uses her Instagram to share her modeling campaigns and share the pictures she takes of other well-known models. She got her start in the fashion world after winning the Harper’s Bazaar (Ukraine) Fashion Award.

karolinakurkova.description: Karolína Kurková is a Czech-American model and actress, best known as a former Victoria’s Secret Angel and Vogue cover star. Mario Testino praised the “proportions of her body and her face, as well as her energy level”, which he said “ma her a model who could fit almost into any moment”. Vogue editor Anna Wintour called her the “next supermodel”. In 2007, Kurková was among the world’s top-earning models, having earned an estimated $5 million. She placed 6th in the Forbes annual list of the highest-earning models that same year.

candicehuffine.description: Classified as a plus-size model, she was signed by IMG and has been featured by magazines such as Vogue and Harper’s Bazaar. Her first major campaign was with Lane Bryant, and she worked with them again on its “I Am No Angel” campaign. During her teenage years, she competed in beauty pageants in both DC and Maryland. She was a cheerleader in school. She signed her first modeling contract when she was 16 years old. While pursuing modeling, she worked side jobs including being a waitress and reservationist to make ends meat.

morganketzner.description: Morgan Ketzner is a famous people who is best known as a Model. Morgan was born on November 1, 1993 in Minnesota. Both she and fellow swimsuit model Petra Nemcova have appeared in Sports Illustrated. Morgan Ketzner is a member of famous Model list. Swimsuit and fashion model who has been featured in several publications including Sports Illustrated. She has amassed over 120,000 followers on her personal morganketzner Instagram account.

yaslenxoxo.description: Yaslen Clemente is notable as an American Instagram star, wellness model and online life character. She came into the spotlight through wonderful looks and body figures which is adored by the individuals. She has a mass measure of fans following on her internet based life like Instagram and Twitter. She is exceptionally well known for her wellness around the globe.

biancataylorm.description: Bianca Taylor is a ISSA certified personal trainer and vegan fitness personality well known for her content on the Instagram account biancataylorm. She has accrued more than 950k followers. In addition to earning her personal trainer certification, she became certified in Plant-based nutrition from ECornell via Cornell University. She hosted a podcast called Badassbabe Radio. She created a second Instagram account with a handle of @biancataylorfitness and also posted similar content to her Instagram on a self-titled YouTube channel.

victoriajustice.description: Victoria Dawn Justice is an American actress and singer. She rose to fame on Nickelodeon in the 2000s, starring as Lola Martinez on Zoey 101 (2005–2008) and later as Tori Vega on Victorious (2010–2013). Justice has also appeared in the films The Boy Who Cried Werewolf (2010), Fun Size (2012), The First Time (2012) and Naomi and Ely’s No Kiss List (2015). In 2015, she starred in the lead role as Lindy Sampson on the MTV television series Eye Candy. karenmcdougal.description: Karen McDougal is an American model and actress. She is known for her appearances in Playboy magazine as Playmate of the Month for December 1997 and Playmate of the Year of 1998. In 2001, the readers of Playboy voted McDougal the runner-up of “The sexiest Playmate of the 1990s”. McDougal taught pre-kindergarten before winning a swimwear competition that launched her career as a glamour, promotional, and swimsuit model. Since her appearances in Playboy, she has extended her career into a wide variety of appearances in mainstream media, including other magazine modeling, television commercials, and minor acting, with mixed success. She has been a successful fitness model, with multiple magazine appearances including being the first woman to appear on the cover of Men’s Fitness magazine. She starred in The Arena, a direct-to-video film, and inspired the creation of a fantasy art statuette and a doll. McDougal is a fitness enthusiast, since having, in her childhood, engaged in ballet study and high school sports. She is an avid motorcycle and car collector. Since her Playmate days, she has maintained a largely private social life. The revelation of an affair with Donald Trump from 2006 to 2007 and its subsequent coverup have put her into national headlines before and after the 2016 United States presidential election.

rachel_nichols.description: Rachel Emily Nichols is an American actress and model. Nichols began modeling while attending Columbia University in New York City in the late 1990s, and transitioned into acting by the early 2000s; she had a part in the romantic drama Autumn in New York (2000) and a one-episode role in the fourth season of Sex and the City (2002). Her first major role was in the comedy Dumb and Dumberer: When Harry Met Lloyd (2003), and she went on to achieve wider recognition playing Rachel Gibson in the final season of the action television series Alias (2005–2006) and for her role in the horror film The Amityville Horror (2005). Nichols obtained her first starring film role in the thriller P2 (2007), and found mainstream success with the science-fiction action films Star Trek (2009) and G.I. Joe: The Rise of Cobra (2009). Her other notable films include The Sisterhood of the Traveling Pants 2 (2008), Conan the Barbarian (2011), Alex Cross (2012), Raze (2013), and Inside (2016). Nichols starred in the television series Continuum (2012–2015), and played notable roles in the sixth season of Criminal Minds (2010–2011), the fourth seasons of both Chicago Fire (2015–2016) and The Librarians (2017–2018), and five episodes as a Gestapo officer named Martha on The Man in the High Castle.

barron.dana.description: Actress Dana Barron is an inspiration to women all around the world who want to pursue their career as an actress. The New York-born actress, Barron got her big break after releasing her TV film National Lampoon’s Christmas Vacation 2: Cousin Eddie’s Island Adventure.

mina_kimes.description: Mina Kimes is an American investigative journalist, sports reporter, senior writer, radio show host and television commentator who currently writes for ‘ESPN The Magazine’ and also appears on multiple television programs and Radio shows. She began her career with ‘Fortune Small Business Magazine’ in 2007 and won several awards and honors for writing about serious topics like arms exports and unauthorized drugs. She joined ‘Bloomberg News’ in 2013 and moved to ESPN the next year. She currently has a lot of roles at ESPN apart from writing; she is a regular panelist on ‘Around the Horn’, a co-host on ‘The Morning Roast’ on ESPN Radio, a guest on ‘The Dan LeBatard Show with Stugotz’ and ‘Highly Questionable’, a debater on ‘First Take’, a contributor to ‘E:60’ and also appears on programs such as ‘Get Up’. In little more than a decade, she has won over a dozen prestigious awards including the ‘Henry R. Luce Award’ and the ‘Front Page Award’.

carleyshimkus.description: Carley Shimkus is a well known American TV correspondent. She is also a well-respected producer and news anchor. kristinfishers.description: Kristin Anne Fisher is an American journalist and television news former presenter and White House correspondent for Fox News. known for her work as the White House correspondent for Fox News. She now works as the Space & Defense correspondent for CNN.

flintstagram77.description: Jill Flint is an American TV and film actress best recognized for appearing as Lana Delaney on CBS’s series ‘The Good Wife’ and as Jill Casey on the USA Network’s series ‘Royal Pains’. The actress has guest starred in a number of TV shows as well, the popular ones being ‘Law & Order: Criminal Intent’, ‘Mercy’, ‘CSI: Miami’ and ‘Elementary’. On the big screen, she has contributed to the movies ‘Garden State’, ‘On Broadway’, ‘The Women’, ‘Cadillac Records’, ‘How I Got Lost’ and ‘The Amazing Spider-Man’. Flint, who is admired for her gorgeous American looks, is a very sweet and charming woman in real life. Her appealing features and bright smile are enough to catch anyone’s attention at a single glance. The American beauty loves being active on Twitter, Instagram, and Facebook, and has hundreds of thousands of fans on these social networking websites.

elvirayourmistress.description: Cassandra Peterson is an American actress best known for playing the vampish character Elvira on the television show ‘Elvira’s Movie Macabre.’ The show was so successful that she has been called ‘Elvira’ ever since! Her popularity peaked with the release of the comedy horror film ‘Elvira, Mistress of the Dark’. She co-wrote and produced the film, as well as its sequel, ‘Elvira’s Haunted Hills’. The character Elvira became so famous that she made several guest appearances on TV shows and movies as Elvira. Before she embarked on an acting career, Cassandra Peterson worked as a dancer in Las Vegas and a pop singer in Italy, singing for an Italian pop-rock band. Peterson made her film debut with a brief role in the James Bond film ‘Diamonds Are Forever’, and was also featured in the role of Queen Sorais in the film ‘Allan Quatermain and the Lost City of Gold’. A gutsy lady, she became the first female to host a national beer ad campaign! Later in her career, she hosted her own reality TV show, ‘The Search for the New Elvira’.

mmarakovits.description: Meredith Marakovits is the New York Yankees’ clubhouse reporter for the YES Network. Marakovits also appears on the network’s special Yankees programming and will contribute to the YESNetwork.com web site.

iamcardib.description: Cardi B is the stage name of American rapper, songwriter, television personality, and actress Belcalis Almánzar who became the only woman to win the Grammy Award for Best Rap Album as a solo artist; she achieved this feat with her debut studio album, Invasion of Privacy. Cardi B established herself as a musical celebrity within a short period of time, following a long struggle throughout her teenage years and early youth, by successfully utilizing her rising fame on social media. Her songs, Bodak Yellow, and I Like It, topped the Billboard Hot 100 chart, while her collaborations with pop band, Maroon 5 (“Girls Like You”) and Bruno Mars (“Finesse” and “Please Me”) reached top three on the list. She also has two mixtapes to her name, Gangsta Bitch Music, Vol. 1 and Vol. 2, and is signed to Atlantic Records. Cardi B was a regular cast on the VH1 reality television series Love & Hip Hop: New York and has made her film debut with Hustlers. Cardi B is immensely popular on Instagram; she has earned more than 85 million followers to her iamcardib account.

billieeilish.description: Billie Eilish is an American singer and songwriter. She is best known for her successful debut single, ‘Ocean Eyes.’ She was born and raised in Los Angeles, California. Belonging to a family of musicians, she was destined to make a career in performing arts. She joined a choir at the age of 8, and by the time she turned 11, she had begun writing and singing her own songs. Her elder brother, Finneas O’Connell, was the biggest influence in her life while she was grew up. He had his own band and had written a song titled ‘Ocean Eyes.’ Billie performed the song and released it online. It became a massive success. This turned out to be her first massive breakthrough. In 2017, her brother helped her record the single ‘Bellyache.’ With the success of the song, Billie released her debut EP, ‘Don’t Smile at Me,’ in August 2017. The EP appeared on several American and international music charts. In October 2017, ‘Apple’ named her their newest ‘Up Next’ artist.

simonegjohnson.description: Simone Johnson is a fashion model, better known as the daughter of Dwayne ‘The Rock’ Johnson. Being the daughter of celebrity parents, it only made sense for Simone to pursue a career in the field of entertainment. However, she has managed to keep her personal life away from the tabloids. She is quite popular on social media platforms and her Instagram account has more than 250,000 followers. Simone shares a special relationship with her father and they are often seen spending quality time together. Simone often accompanies her father to major red carpet events. At the 43rd ‘People’s Choice Awards,’ Simone appeared in an elegant black dress and was seen congratulating her father on winning an award at the event. Thanks to her popularity, Simone was chosen as the first ambassador of ‘Golden Globe Awards.’

Another exciting fact but out of context is that there is another fictional character similar to her name in a crime novel, The Godfather written by Mario Puzo.

madisonlintz.description: Madison Lintz is a popular American actress who gained much fame as a child actress for her role in the horror drama television series ‘The Walking Dead’. Her portrayal of the character Sophia Peletier in the highly popular series made Madison a well-known child actress of the 2010s. For this role, the little girl was nominated for a Young Artist Award in the category Best Performance in a TV Series – Supporting Young Actress. Born to an actress mother, Madison was exposed to the glitz and glamor of the show biz world at a young age. Her mom introduced her to the field of acting when the girl was just six years old. Literally growing up in front of the camera, it did not take long for her to blossom into a confident performer. She began her career by doing commercials and first gained notice when one of her commercials for a national Golden Corral spot was aired all over the United States. When she was 11 years old, she was selected to play the role of Sophia in the television series ‘The Walking Dead.’ The success of the series led to other acting offers and soon she ventured into films as well, playing supporting roles in the movies ‘Parental Guidance’ and ‘After.’

A native of California, Zhavia harbored musical aspirations since she was a child. She was inspired by the likes of Wiz Khalifa and Post Malone as well as by her parents, who were both singers. She started off her career as a singer by performing at talent shows and open mic challenges and later landed an opportunity to be a part of the Urban Music Department of the OC Hit Factory, which is a recording academy run by producer Thomas Barsoe. In 2018, she appeared as a contestant on the first season of Fox’s reality television music competition series ‘The Four: Battle for Stardom’ and finished the series as one of the finalists. Since then, she has put out two singles, ‘Candlelight’ and ‘Deep Down,’ and has collaborated with Diplo, French Montana and Lil Pump on the song ‘Welcome to the Party’ for the soundtrack of the superhero film ‘Deadpool 2’.
