brightonsharbino.description: Brighton Sharbino is an American actress best known for her role in the horror drama series ‘The Walking Dead’. Her career began with a guest role in the show ‘Friday Night Light’, a drama series which was based on a football team in a fictional town. She continued to appear in guest roles in other series as well, such as ‘Hannah Montana’ and ‘NCIS’. She became well-known after she began playing a recurring role in the horror drama series ‘The Walking Dead’ in 2013. She played the role of Lizzie Samuels in the fourth and fifth seasons of the series. Meanwhile, she also appeared in two episodes of the crime anthology series ‘True Detective’. She has appeared in several movies as well. Her big screen credits include ‘The Death of Socrates’, ‘Cheap Thrills’ and ‘Miracles from Heaven’. After playing numerous minor film roles, she bagged the lead role in the film ‘Urban City’.

espnhannahstorm.description: Hannah Storen Hicks known professionally as Hannah Storm, is an American television sports journalist, serving as the anchor of ESPN’s SportsCenter Face to Face. She was also host of the NBA Countdown pregame show on ABC as part of the network’s NBA Sunday game coverage. She is also the play-by-play announcer on Amazon Prime Video during Thursday Night Football with Andrea Kremer.

mskellyprice.description: Who knew singing in church as a toddler will bring you the stardom. Today we will be talking about Kelly Price. She made a name for herself as a backing and guest vocalist, appearing on a number hit singles.

biancalbeltran.description: Active in the journalism field for years, the lady is equally beautiful and hardworking. Her hard work and dedication helped her to reach the point where she has earned both name and fame. She is non-other than Bianca Beltran.

_elle_johnson.description: Elle Johnson is an American Model from Park City, Utah who has modeled for Sports Illustrated. She appears to be a supporter of University of Michigan as many of her photos show her to be a supporter of the Football team. She has a strong following on Instagram and Twitter.

natashabertrand.description: Natasha Bertrand is an American journalist. She is a National Security Correspondent for Politico. Bertrand is also a Contributor to NBC News and MSNBC. Natasha Bertrand began her career in 2014 at Business Insider , where she worked her way up from intern to political correspondent. Bertrand joined the staff of The Atlantic in early 2018, and shortly thereafter signed on as a Contributor to NBC News and MSNBC. In March 2019, she left The Atlantic to join Politico as a National Security Correspondent. She has written several articles about the Trump administration including “Felix Sater to testify after missing previously scheduled appearance “, “Spies fear a consulting firm helped hobble U.S. intelligence “, and “Trump’s House allies lie in wait for Mueller” in July 2019.

erinryder13.description: Erin Ryder is an American television host, television producer, adventurer, explorer and photographer. She was a co-executive producer and on-camera investigator for Syfy’s hit reality television series Destination Truth, a weekly one-hour show filmed in remote locations around the world that explored some of the world’s mysteries and unexplained phenomena. She also served as a host and co-executive producer on the series Chasing UFOs for the National Geographic Channel.

brittneyatwood.description: The sexy Brittney Atwood is a YouTuber and features mostly in her husband’s vlogs. She is married to Roman Atwood, who is a YouTube sensation with millions of subscribers to his channel. He regularly films vlogs along with his girlfriend Brittney, who lives with him. The couple has two children: a son named Kane Alexander Atwood and a daughter named Cora Atwood. She has a channel of her own that goes by her name where she vlogs personally. However, she is more popularly known for her husband’s vlogs. She is a mega sensation on Instagram with over 2.4 million followers, and has over 910K fans on Twitter as well. The couple became a huge sensation with their ‘prank videos. The duo was in a relationship for 10 years before they got married in July 2018.

shibani_joshi.description: There are only a few people who manage to maintain the balance between their work and personal life. Many of the experts fail to do so. Today, the biography is about such a person who maintains a perfect balance between her professional and personal life. She is progressing in her career and at the same time is having a happy married life.

babybushwhacked.description: Brooke Bush is an American YouTube star and social media personality. She has gained fame for posting vlogs on her self-titled YouTube channel. A Kentucky native, Bush set up her channel in April 2013 and began posting content on it two years later. Since then, her channel has grown exponentially and currently boasts of over 360k subscribers and tens of millions of total views. Her vlogs generally revolve around her family, friends, travels, and college life. Her popularity on YouTube has found its way to other social media platforms as well. She has over a hundred thousand followers on the @babybushwhacked Instagram account and a few thousand followers on Twitter.

gretchenmenn.description: Gretchen Menn is an American guitarist and composer who has her own original instrumental work and is also the lead guitarist for Zepparella, an all-female Led Zeppelin tribute band. She was included in Guitar Player Magazine’s ’50 Sensational Female Guitarists and Guitar Player Magazine’s ’50 Years of Extraordinary Players. In 2017 she was one of 11 female guitarists selected to contribute a track onto She Rocks, Vol. 1, a compilation released on Steve Vai’s label: ‘Favored Nations’. In 2017 she was nominated by readers of Vintage Guitar Magazine as ‘Artist of the Year’, alongside Allan Holdsworth, Steve Vai, Dan Auerbach, Rik Emmett, and Andy Timmons. She has provided lessons for Acoustic Guitar Magazine, JamPlay – an online guitar lesson provider, and has been a 3-time counselor at Rock and Roll Fantasy Camps.

elenigiokos.description: Eleni Giokos is CNNMoney Africa correspondent based in Johannesburg. She reported from key global events such as the World Economic Forum in Davos and the United Nations General Assembly, and chaired debates at Davos, WEF Africa, the International Monetary Fund, African Finance Corporation and the Africa CEO Forum.

cristinaalesci.description: Cristina Alesci is a CNN and CNNMoney correspondent based out of the network’s New York bureau. She covers breaking news for the network as well as financial fraud and controversies facing major companies. Her investigative series focuses on public policy issues of the 2016 election cycle, food production, and documenting the early struggles of successful leaders.

mollybrazy.description: Molly Brazy is an American rap artist. She is popularly known for her chartbuster tracks ‘More Facts’ and ‘Gang.’ She rose to prominence after she was featured on the ‘YouTube’ channel owned by the independent American magazine ‘4sho Magazine.’ All her music is available on this channel. Her music reflects her troubled childhood. Molly is sometimes regarded as one of the most controversial stars in the American rap scene. Her rebellious nature and her love for firearms have brought her a lot of negative publicity. Molly was once involved in a controversy after a video showing her pointing a gun at a toddler became viral. The controversy made several headlines. Amid this chaos, Molly released her debut mixtape. The mixtape, however, was a success.

darceysilva.description: Darcey Silva is an American television personality, entrepreneur, clothing designer and actress. She is best known for her role on TLC’s reality television shows 90 Day Fiancé: Before the 90 Days and Darcey & Stacey.

vmsalama.description: Life is about maintaining a balance between personal and professional life. And Vivian Salama, the journalist is one individual who is capable enough to maintain a balance between the two. Salama has collected vast experience from several organizations and at the same time, has earned a good amount of net worth and salary.

katemansi.description: Daytime Emmy Award-winning, American actress, Kate Mansi has won the hearts of millions of fans with her role in the several movies and TV series. Her innocent face and cute smiles help her to earn a great fan following.

kerenswan.description: Keren Swanson is an American YouTube star and social media influencer. She has gained fame for her two YouTube channels, KKandbabyJ and Keren Swan, where she posts family-related videos and lifestyle vlogs. A native of Georgia, Keren was primarily raised in Florida. She met her future fiancé Khoa Nguyen while they both were in high school. They dated on and off through their late teens and early twenties before they moved in together. During this period, they did several off-the-wall jobs to support themselves. In November 2012, they set up their joint channel, KkandbabyJ, and in April 2015, uploaded their first video. In February 2016, she created her self-titled personal channel. It was not long before their channels gained traction. As of 2018, their main channel has accumulated over a million subscribers and more than 300 million views. On her personal channel, Keren has about 415 thousand subscribers and 30 million views.

claire_hosterman.description: Claire Hosterman is the older sister of Disney Channel star, Dove Cameron, and a singer. She studied voice for over ten years in Seattle, New York City, Los Angeles, and Paris before taking up voice training as a profession. Today, she teaches singing to students of all ages at beginners’ level at her voice studio, helping them with the right technique for all styles of singing, including Pop, Rock, Musical Theatre, R&B, and Opera. She uses a kinaesthetic and holistic approach to singing, tailoring lessons to each individual student’s requirements. Her initial success encouraged her to go a step further and take her studio online through Skype to reach out to enthusiastic singers throughout the globe. She has a large following on social media.

jojo_babie.description: If you are into a curvy body, fashionable and sexy model then this article is definitely for you. Today we are going to talk about the Instagram star who earned a name for herself out of her diva look and undeniably sexy body. Jojo Babie aka Jojo von South is an Asian Instagram model. sabrinaclaudio.description: Sabrina Claudio is an American singer and songwriter managed by SAL&CO/Neal Atweh. In late 2016, Claudio uploaded several songs to SoundCloud, before compiling a select collection as part of her debut extended play, Confidently Lost, which was released independently in March 2017. Her single “Unravel Me” peaked at number 22 on the Billboard Twitter Emerging Artists chart, and her single “Belong to You” peaked at number two on the same. Her debut mixtape, About Time was released on October 5, 2017. It peaked at number 13 on Billboard’s Top R&B/Hip-Hop Albums chart.

qimmahrusso.description: Fitness professional and trainer who runs Q-Flex Fitness with the intention of bringing motivation, intensity, happiness, education, inspiration, togetherness, and love of oneself to being healthy and fit. She had a popular Vine account as well.

lily_marston.description: Lily Marston is a widely-recognized name amongst the YouTube community. She is closely associated with fellow YouTuber and comedian, Shane Dawson. Lily began her career in acting with her first performance in a TV mini-series in 2014 called Beauty Breaks where she appeared alongside Meghan Rienks. The year 2015 saw her bagging the lead role in another TV mini-series called ‘Throwback’ where she got the chance of performing with Ryland Adams and Miriam Isa. In 2016, she also became a part of the popular show ‘Clevver Now’ where she acted along with Ryland Adams yet another time. She featured along with Drew Dorsey and Joslyn Davis, and is believed to be quite close to them. She was recently seen preparing for the shoot of another sitcom Hair Spray Live in the Universal Studios.

plazadeaubrey.description: Aubrey Christina Plaza is an American actress, comedian, and producer. She began her career performing improv and sketch comedy at the Upright Citizens Brigade Theater. She starred as April Ludgate on the NBC sitcom Parks and Recreation (2009–2015), and later featured in the FX drama series Legion (2017–2019). Plaza had her first leading film role in Safety Not Guaranteed (2012). She also starred in the films Mystery Team (2009), Funny People (2009), Scott Pilgrim vs. the World (2010), Monsters University (2013), Life After Beth (2014), Dirty Grandpa (2016), Mike and Dave Need Wedding Dates (2016), The Little Hours (2017), Ingrid Goes West (2017), An Evening with Beverly Luff Linn (2018), Child’s Play (2019), Happiest Season (2020), and Black Bear (2020).

jasmincadavid.description: Internationally published urban model, video vixen, realtor, and entrepreneur. She has also been featured in music videos. In her school days she played soccer and softball, ran cross country and track. She didn’t know that could translate into a modeling jobs. She won the Urban Model Award for Video Vixen of the Year in 2015.

amouranth.description: Kaitlyn Siragusa is an American model, professional cosplayer, and entrepreneur. Kaitlyn Siragusa is a Twitch streamer, character entertainer, and own entertainment channel named, ‘A Charmed Affair’. She is also a social media star active on sites like Facebook, Twitter, and Instagram. her Instagram accounts have gained followers over 3.2million. She has amassed over 416.5k followers with additional links of Gmail and Patreon accounts.

trulykenya.description: Kenya Duke is the owner of Premier Sports and Corporate Travel, a successful travel management company. Besides, Duke is also famous for Athletes and Entertainers for arranging all the traveling resources. Staying on the other side of the glamorous industry, Duke is the owner of Premier Sports and Corporate Travel Company as well.

emmacaulfieldofficial.description: Emma Caulfield Ford is an American actress known for her role as Anya Jenkins on the television series Buffy the Vampire Slayer (1998–2003), as well as Susan Keats, a love interest of Brandon Walsh’s, on the television series Beverly Hills, 90210. Her film roles include Darkness Falls (2003) and Timer (2009).

juliaroberts.description: We all believe in a dream, which we want to convert into reality. Similarly, Julia Robert also had a dream to become a veterinarian as a child. chloemelas.description: Chloe Melas is a CNN entertainment reporter based in New York. She is well known for her work on the HollywoodLife pop culture and has won wild popularity as an anchor.

alyseeadyfox5.description: Alyse Eady is an American news anchor and a titleholder of Miss Arkansas 2010. Also, she became first runner-up at the pageant Miss America 2011. Eady serves as an anchor of Fox  News in Good Day Atlanta of Fox 5 Atlanta WAGA-TV

robinthede.description: Robin Thede, especially an American comedian is also recognized as an actress, writer, sketch artist, and improvisational comedian. She worked at The Nightly Show. She was the first African- American women to be the head writer for a late-night talk show. Additionally, Robin starred in BET original web series Buppies.

veronicawebb.description: A prominent American model Veronica Webb has successfully established herself as an actress, writer, and television personality. She is the first African-American women to have a major cosmetics contract. Also, Webb has appeared in some famous magazines including Vogue, Essence, and Eile magazines and on the runway for Victoria’s Secret.

sarahshahi.description: “Beauty isn’t about having a pretty face, it’s about having a pretty mind, pretty heart and pretty soul”. Related to this thought, here we will present an actress with an equal balance of beauty and a brain. She is none other than Sarah Shahi. Sarah is an Iranian-American television actress.

daniellefishel.description: Danielle Christine Fishel is an American actress, director, model, and television personality. She began her career in theater, appearing in community productions of The Wizard of Oz and Peter Pan. She made her debut as an actress shortly after, making guest appearances in shows such as Full House and Harry and the Hendersons. In 1993, Fishel was cast for the role as Topanga Lawrence-Matthews on the teen sitcom Boy Meets World, which ran on ABC, and reprised the role for its successor Girl Meets World on Disney Channel, which aired from 2014 to 2017. Fishel was the host of Style Network’s The Dish, and appears in National Lampoon’s Dorm Daze, as well as its sequel. She was a spokeswoman for Nutrisystem, and is also a resident reporter on PopSugar, and on their spin-off YouTube channel, PopSugar Girls Guide.

elizberkley.description: Elizabeth Berkley is an American actress, philanthropist, and producer. Her most notable roles were Jessie Spano in the television series Saved by the Bell, and Nomi Malone in the 1995 Paul Verhoeven film Showgirls. She is also known for the title role in the English dub of the anime film Armitage III: Poly-Matrix, and her supporting roles in the films The First Wives Club and Roger Dodger. In theater, she received critical acclaim for her performance in Hurlyburly.

andidorfman.description: Andi Dorfman is an American television personality, author, and attorney. She was a contestant on the eighteenth season of The Bachelor, and the lead on tenth season of The Bachelorette. She became famous for walking out on bachelor Juan Pablo Galavis in the ninth episode of The Bachelor. She became the first former attorney to appear as The Bachelorette.

cierraramirez.description: From there birth, some people come to the earth with unique talent and some people with multi-talent. In Cierra Ramirez’s case, she came into the earth taking the second one option. Cierra is both, an actor and a musician. From her singing talent, she came into fam. The beauty and talented lady has worked with great names and has played in many series and movies such as Girl In Progress, The Fosters, and The Secret Life of the American Teenager.

leeanntweeden.description: Leeann Tweeden is an American radio broadcaster, model and sports commentator. Since, February 2017, she has been the newscaster for McIntyre in the Morning on Radio 790 KABC in Los Angeles.

auliicravalho.description: Auliʻi Cravalho is an American actress and singer who made her acting debut as the titular character in the 2016 Disney computer animated musical feature film Moana. She went on to star in the NBC drama series Rise (2018) and the Netflix drama film All Together Now (2020).

oliviataylordudley.description: Olivia Taylor Dudley is an American actress. She is known for her horror film roles such as Chernobyl Diaries (2012), The Vatican Tapes (2015) and Paranormal Activity: The Ghost Dimension (2015), for her television roles such as the Syfy fantasy series The Magicians, and for her work in the internet sketch group 5-Second Films.

anyataylorjoy.description: Anya Taylor-Joy is a British-Argentine actress who is best recognized for her roles in the horror films ‘The Witch’, ‘Split’ and ‘Glass’. Her popular roles in the horror movies have conferred upon her the title of “scream queen”. Born in US to an English-Spanish photographer and interior designer, and a Scottish-Argentine banker, Joy relocated to Argentina as an infant. At the age of six, she moved to London where she received her education before being scouted as a model at the age of 16. Taylor-Joy, who has received Cannes Film Festival’s Trophée Chopard, is a multitalented woman. She is good at playing the electric guitar and ukulele and is also a trained ballet dancer. A loving sister of five behind the curtains, the gorgeous lady is undoubtedly a quickly rising superstar. On a personal note, she is a family-oriented girl. She is a die-hard fan of British actor Eddie Redmayne and cites him as her major cinematic crush.

neriahfisherfan.description: Neriah Fisher is a famous American YouTuber who always posts various types of makeup tutorials, fashions tips, and cover songs on her self-titled YouTube channel having over 57K subscribers. She is also recognized as a famous Instagram personality. Also, she released a couple of songs like Ride Away, I Kissed a Girl, If I Were a Boy, Cloud 9, and I Don’t Wanna Live Forever. emilydeschanel.description: Emily Deschanel is a famous American actress who is also known as a director and producer. Deschanel is known for her role of Dr. Temperance Brennan in the television series ‘Bones’ on Fox Channel. From 2005 to 2017, she appeared in the series.

1capplegate.description: Christina Applegate is an American actress and a dancer. As a minor actress, she began playing the role of Kelly Bundy on the Fox sitcom Married… with Children (1987–97). In her grown-up years, Applegate established her film and television career, winning an Emmy Award. Also, she got Tony and Golden Globe nominations.

torriewilson.description: Torrie Wilson is a retired American professional wrestler, fitness competitor, and model, best known for her work with World Wrestling Entertainment (WWE). As a fitness competitor, Wilson won the Miss Galaxy competition in 1998. Shortly after, she was signed by World Championship Wrestling, where she stayed from 1999 until 2001. In 2001, she began appearing on World Wrestling Federation (WWF) television as part of The Invasion storyline. Her most high-profile storyline took place in 2003 when she feuded with Dawn Marie. Wilson has also been a part of the all-female stable, or group of affiliated wrestlers, known as Vince’s Devils, which ended its run in 2006. Aside from wrestling, Wilson has been on the cover of several magazines, including FHM and Playboy, which she posed for twice.

soniagranados.description: Sonia Granados is a Social worker as well as an actress who is recognized for Dead Giveaway (2013) and Btwn2Flrs (2016).

melissabenoist.description: Melissa Marie Benoist is an American actress, singer, and dancer. She has acted on stage and in television and film. Moreover, she recognized for her portrayal of the titular character in the CBS/CW DC Comics-based superhero drama series Supergirl (2015–present).

princesstagram.description: A talented and hardworking woman Maya Rudolph is a comedian, voice artist, singer, and a renowned actress. Currently, she is introducing her singing ability in The Rentals. Later, she joined NBC television as a cast member in the series Saturday Night Live. She has appeared in several movies which includes Grown Ups (2010), Bridesmaids (2011), Grown Ups 2 (2013), and Sisters (2015). Additionally, she has lent her voice to the animated movie Shrek the Third (2007) and Big Hero 6(2014).

tanitaa.st.description: Not everyone gets the chance to fall in love, twice or thrice in life. However, the former American professional football player Michael Strahan found love not once or twice but thrice. You must be wondering why we are talking about Michael but you must know the fact that Tanita Strahan is the daughter of a famous football player Michael. Her father spent all of his 15-year careers in the National Football League (NFL) with the New York Giants.

ryanashleymalarkey.description: Ryan Ashley DiCristina is an American tattoo artist known for her appearances on the television shows Ink Master and its spin-offs. Her signature style reflects her training and experience as a fashion designer: Malarkey specializes in black-and-gray designs with beadwork, lace detail, and ornamental jewels. Malarkey won Ink Master’s season eight competition in 2016 and in the following three years, hosted two seasons of a spin-off show (Angels) and served as a judge in another spin-off (Grudge Match). Malarkey also owns two oddities and antiques shops in Pennsylvania.

jennytaft.description: Jenny Taft is a media personality who also is an American reporter best known for her work at Fox News. She began her career as an on-air host for Fox Sports North. Moreover, Taft hosted the show, Minnesota Wild. After that, she started working as a host in Minnesota Twins (May 2012). Currently, she is working only for FOX Sports 1 as a reporter and host. Her fame boosted with her outstanding work and dedication.

jennaelfman.description: Jenna Elfman is an American actress, who is known for her performance in television comedies, such as ‘Dharma & Greg’ and ‘ Accidentally on Purpose’. A California native, Elfman was a student at California State University, Northridge (CSUN). When she was five years old, she began training in ballet. However, she was eventually forced to quit after the tendon separated from her bone. At the beginning of her professional career, she was a dancer and appeared in various music videos. She made her screen debut as an actor in a 1992 episode of ‘Murder, She Wrote’. Elfman landed her first leading role in 1996 in the ABC sitcom ‘Townies’. A year later, she made her cinematic debut in the action-comedy film ‘Grosse Pointe Blank’. Her most well-known outing was the ABC sitcom ‘Dharma & Greg’, for which she earned three Primetime Emmy nominations and a Golden Globe Award for Best Actress – Television Series Musical or Comedy in 1999. At present, Elfman is part of the main cast of the AMC horror-drama series ‘Fear the Walking Dead’.

sophiebeem.description: Sophie Beem is an American singer and songwriter from New York City. Born and raised in Manhattan’s Upper East Side, she released music under Parkwood Entertainment after being signed by Beyoncé to a two-year artist development deal in 2016. Beem auditioned for The X Factor US in 2012, where she performed for judges Britney Spears, Demi Lovato, Simon Cowell and L.A. Reid. jamiejchung.description: Jamie Chung is an American actress and former reality television personality who gained fame as a cast member on the MTV reality series The Real World: San Diego and subsequently through her appearances on its spin-off show, Real World/Road Rules Challenge: The Inferno II in 2004. genirodriguez.description: Genesis Rodriguez is an American actress who is famous for playing many leading roles in the Telemundo telenovelas, Prisionera (2004), Dame Chocolate (2007) and Doña Bárbara (2008–2009). In 2014, Rodriguez also provided her voice for the character Honey Lemon in Disney’s Big Hero 6.

briannehowey.description: Brianne Nicole Howey is an American actress. She has appeared as a series regular on the Fox supernatural horror The Exorcist (2016) and the Fox thriller The Passage (2019), in addition to a recurring role on The CW superhero drama Batwoman (2019–present). Howey has also portrayed one of the leads of the Netflix comedy-drama Ginny & Georgia since 2021.

dreeandree.description: Andrée ‘Dre’ Vermeulen is an American actress who plays Dr. Monica Scholls in the TBS comedy series Angie Tribeca. She also voices the character Ruffnut in DreamWorks Dragons. Vermeulen studied drama at Marymount Manhattan College and started her career with the Upright Citizens Brigade in 2008 in New York City and continued her work with them after her move to Los Angeles two years later. She is skilled at freestyle rapping in her UCB performances and cites Dana Carvey, Lil Wayne, and Q-Tip (musician) as influences. She credits her improv training for helping her get the role on Angie Tribeca, saying that understanding “the game of the scene” was essential to the Scholls character.

blaironealgolf.description: Stepping away from the trend and trying different thing in life is not everyone’s cup of tea. Yet, the star that we are going to talk about is someone who chose the career way different than any normal ladies that will prefer to do. The star proves herself as an example worthy to bring down the stereotypes.

hanamaelee.description: Hana Mae Lee is an American actress, model, comedian, and fashion designer. She is best known for playing the role of Lilly Onakuramara in the musical comedy Pitch Perfect film series (2012–2017) and the role of Sonya in the horror comedy film The Babysitter (2017) and its 2020 sequel. Lee also owns the fashion line Hanamahn.

lauriesegall.description: Laurie Segall is an American journalist who is a senior technology reporter for CNN and editor at large for CNN Tech. She is also the host of Mostly Human, a docu-series that explores the impact of technology on sex, love, and death. Moreover, she interviews CEOs and people who influence current tech-world. She has also sat in a QNA session Microsoft’s owner and once the world’s richest man Bill Gates.

taylormomsen.description: Taylor Momsen is an American musician, singer, model, and former actress who is known for portraying the character of Jenny Humphrey on The CW’s teen drama series, Gossip Girl (2007–2012). Moreover, she played the role of Cindy Lou Who in the film, How the Grinch Stole Christmas (2000). Momsen is also known for being the lead singer and frontwoman of the American rock band, The Pretty Reckless.

andranechita.description: They say Optimism is the faith that leads to success. Nothing can be done without hope and confidence in today’s world. mizuopeck.description: Mizuo Peck is a prominent American actress, best known for her role of Sacagawea in Night at the Museum. Also, she appeared in many movies such as Scenes of the Crime, A Case of You, and many more.

leighkoechner.description: Leigh Koechner is a multitalented American actress, host, speaker, podcaster, author as well as comedian. Koechner is mostly known for her character in the TV series The Comebacks, Combat Missions and Wild Girls Gone. Currently, she is the Host of 33 with Leigh.

carolcostello.description: If one will go on listing the popular news anchor’s names, then for sure, they will never miss, Carol Costello. Carol Costello is an American news anchor and former host of CNN Newsroom, currently working for HLN.

Moreover, she played the role of Dr. Meredith Fell in The CW fantasy drama, The Vampire Diaries (2012-2013) and as Carrie in The CW drama, One Tree Hill (2008-2009).

melissaleeontv.description: The News Anchor for CNBC, Melissa Lee is a prominent journalist who is widely known for occasionally hosting Closing Bell. Moreover, Lee has also hosted Options Action and is now hosting CNBC’s daily Currency Trading show Fast Money and Money in Motion at 5.

paigexmackenzie.description: Paige Mackenzie is an American professional golfer who played on the LPGA Tour. She played on the LPGA Tour and has also won exempt status in the 2007 LPGA Tour season. She also becomes an NAPW Athletic Spokeswoman.

heather_tesch.description: Fame and name don’t come so easily. To become a famous person, we should put a lot of dedication, hard work and believe in ourselves. Moreover, she played the role of a President of the United States in the science fiction film, Independence Day: Resurgence in 2016.

bettywliu.description: The award-winning business reporter, Betty Liu regularly interviews important business person, political and media leaders. She has interviewed two former US Presidents, Jimmy Carter, and Bill Clinton and as well as Warren Buffet, and Carlos Slim. She is more fluent in Mandarin, and also speaks Cantonese Chinese and other some languages, so people also called her multi-talented media lady.

stephanieabrams.description: Stephanie Abrams is an American television meteorologist who has worked for The Weather Channel (TWC) since 2003. She currently co-hosts AMHQ with Jen Carfagno and Jim Cantore early weekday mornings.

evargastv.description: Emmy Award-winning American television personality, Elizabeth Vargas is widely known for being lead investigative reporter/documentary anchor for A&E Networks. After being an anchor of ABC’s 20/20 television news magazine and ABC News specials for the past 14 years, she began her new position in 2018.

maryelizabethmcglynn.description: Mary Elizabeth McGlynn is an American voice actress, ADR director and singer-songwriter best known for her involvement in music production in multiple games from the Silent Hill series, and her extensive English-language dubbing of various anime, animated films and video games.

madelinebrewerr.description: Madeline Kathryn Brewer is an American actress. She is known for her role as Tricia Miller in the Emmy award-winning series Orange Is the New Black (2013), her role in Hemlock Grove (2014–2015), and her lead role as Alice/Lola in the Netflix horror film Cam. She stars as Janine Lindo in the Hulu series The Handmaid’s Tale (2017–present), which earned her an Emmy nomination for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Drama Series.

nikkireed.description: Nikki Reed is an American actress, screenwriter, singer-songwriter, and model who is well known for her portrayal of vampire Rosalie Hale in The Twilight Saga. Moreover, she made her appearance in the film, Thirteen, along with Catherine Hardwicke as a co-writer of the screenplay, and in which she an Independent Spirit Award for Best Debut Performance, as well as many nominations in 2003.

jennifer.westhoven.description: Jennifer Westhoven is an American reporter, currently a correspondent for HLN. She covers the economy, business, personal finance and money topics. She has been with the CNN network since 2000, starting with CNNfn. She previously worked for Reuters from 1993 to 2000. Since 2006, she has been a part of the HLN morning show Morning Express with Robin Meade. Her regular segment throughout the morning on “Morning Express” and the Mid-Morning Block of HLN is called Your Money. She also appears regularly in the network’s weekend Clark Howard show and fills in anchoring HLN’s weekend newscasts. Now based in Atlanta, she formerly reported from CNN’s NYC headquarters, as well as the New York Stock Exchange and NASDAQ. She is also a contributor to the weekend CNN program Your Money, which airs on Saturday and Sunday afternoons. Westhoven grew up in Cranford, New Jersey and earned a Bachelor of Arts degree in history and political science from Bryn Mawr College.

poppyharlowcnn.description: Poppy Harlow is an American reporter, producer, and journalist, best known for reporting at CNN and Forbes. Moreover, she is an anchor of CNN Newsroom and CNN’s New York news bureau. Previously, she was a business correspondent at CNN, CNN International, and HLN, an anchor for CNNMoney, and a Forbes Video Network anchor. Also, she is a weekday relief presenter for CNN’s New Day early-morning news program.

mackenziefoy.description: Mackenzie Foy is an American actress and model with a successful position across the entertainment industry. She is known by her work in Breaking Dawn: Part 2 as the character of Renesmee Cullen. At the age of 18, her work from that movie led her to earn a Young Artist Award. Further, Foy has achieved many awards and nominations in her lifetime.

dorisaburke.description: Doris Burke is an American sports announcer and analyst for NBA on ESPN, NBA on ABC, College Basketball on ESPN, and College Basketball on ABC games. She formerly worked as an analyst for WNBA games on MSG, and has worked on New York Knicks games. Burke was the first female commentator to call a New York Knicks game on radio and television. Burke played college basketball for the Providence Friars, finishing her career as the school’s leader in assists. Honored for her pioneering work, she was selected to enter the Basketball Hall of Fame as the 2018 Curt Gowdy Media Award winner.

lynnsmithtv.description: Lynn Smith is an American anchor for HLN, she also has served as a host of Weekend Express. As of now, she has won the Media Award, Mothers Against Drunk Driving. Famous HLN reporter Lynn Smith has amassed a huge amount of net worth from her successful career in journalism.

lilireinhart.description: Gifted with beautiful vocals and acting skill, this rising star is quickly imposing herself as a force to reckon. rosalindruthross.description: Rosalind Ross is an American actress and writer, best known for her work in The Contract, Matador and Escaping North Korea: Defiance and Hope in the World’s Most Repressive Country.

Described as “one of the most powerful women in Washington,” Yellin began reporting for CNN as the network’s senior political correspondent in 2007, covering Capitol Hill, domestic politics and the White House. Her debut novel, Savage News, was published in April 2019.

toniyates7.description: Toni Yates is an American news reporter and anchorwoman who works for Eyewitness News WABC-TV as the New Jersey reporter. She is Eyewitness of News’ New Jersey Reporter, usually seen at Noon, 5 PM or 6 PM.

teyonahparris.description: Teyonah Parris is an American actress. She began her career playing secretary Dawn Chambers in the AMC drama series Mad Men (2012–2015) and starring in the 2014 independent film Dear White People. Since that, Parris starred in Spike Lee’s film Chi-Raq, in US soap opera Empire and in Academy-nominated film If Beale Street Could Talk. In 2021, Parris landed her breakthrough role portraying an adult Monica Rambeau in the Marvel Cinematic Universe Disney+ series WandaVision. She will reprise the role in The Marvels, scheduled to be released in 2022. Parris has won two Black Reel Awards and received nominations at Screen Actors Guild Awards and NAACP Image Awards.

patriciaarquette.description: Patricia Arquette is an American actress who is famous for her feature debut film as Kristen Parker in A Nightmare on Elm Street 3: Dream Warriors (1987). kimoraleesimmons.description: Kimora Lee Leissner is a well-known fashion model and fashion designer from the United States. She is popularly known as the ex-wife of Kimora Lee Leissner. Further, she is also known as the reality televisions star for Kimora: Life in the Fab Lane, on The E! Channel and Style Network.

maggiegeha.description: Maggie Geha is a gorgeous American actress and model. She is well known for working in the soap opera All My Children in the year 2013 and is seen across televisions, music videos and magazines and prints.

meganhenderson.description: Megan Henderson is an American broadcast journalist. She joined KTLA, the CW affiliate in Los Angeles, in March 2009 and anchors the station’s weekday morning news. Before KTLA, she anchored the morning news at Fox station KDFW in Dallas and Fox station KSTU in Salt Lake City. She also guest-hosted several episodes of the Fox News Channel’s Fox & Friends Weekend in 2008.

adriannacosta.description: Adrianna Costa is an American television personality best known as an entertainment reporter and a reality show host.

hudsonanne.description: Originally from Bowling Green, Kentucky, Anne Hudson‘s talent shines all around the world, and her viewers have their eyes glued on her. With unique facial features, it can be assured that she is one of the most beautiful anchors.

christinaparktv.description: Christina Park is a Korean and American news anchor, best known as a Forbes contributor who writes about business, leadership and the workplace. In the process, she inspires others and widely recognizes to the world by her unique strengths and abilities. Currently, Park working for Fox5 as an anchor.

juliebenzmft.description: Julie Benz is an American actress, best known for her roles as Darla on Buffy the Vampire Slayer and Angel (1997–2004) and Rita Bennett on Dexter (2006–2010), for which she won the 2006 Satellite Award for Best Supporting Actress and the 2009 Saturn Award for the same category.

stefanialavieowen.description: Stefania LaVie Owen is a New Zealand-American actress. She is known for her roles as Puddle Kadubic in the television series Running Wilde and as Dorrit Bradshaw in the teen drama television series The Carrie Diaries. She starred as Melanie in the film Paper Spiders, as Bear in the Netflix show Sweet Tooth, and as Nicole Chance in the Hulu original psychological thriller Chance.

fredrickawhitfield.description: Fredricka Whitfield is an American news anchor and reporter, currently working for CNN. Likewise, she served for several tv stations including NBC News, WPLG-TV, KTVT-TV, WCIV and many more. Being hardworking and responsible, she has been honored with more than eight prestigious awards.

wendyburch.description: Wendy Ann Burch is an American television journalist, advocate and professional writer. Burch has been awarded six Emmy Awards from the Television Academy, as well as an Excellence in Journalism Award from the Alliance of Women in Media. Burch has worked at number of local news stations in major television markets throughout the United States. She is currently a correspondent for the award-winning KTLA Morning News in Los Angeles, and is one of the most-recognized reporters in the Los Angeles area; the second-largest media market in the country.

shamicka_lawrence.description: There are many people who, despite sharing more than a decade long relationship fail to manage it. The same case is with the ex-wife of an American stand-up comedian, actor, producer, and writer Martin Lawrence, Shamicka Gibbs.

sarahaines.description: Every single person in this world is talented but you must be able to know your “why”. That’s what Sara Haines did, she found her desire. You must be wondering who this Sara is right? Don’t worry we are here to clear your all the doubts and curiosity. She is one of the most appreciated and loved TV personalities. Today we are going to talk about Haines who is one of the most influential TV hosts.

msshaunrobinson.description: Shaun Robinson is an American television host, author, producer, philanthropist, television personality and actress. She is perhaps best known for hosting Access Hollywood (1999–2015) and 90 Day Fiancé (2016–present). Her accolades include an Emmy Award for her live coverage of A Grand Night in Harlem for the Black Sports and Entertainment Hall of Fame.

tracelysette.description: Trace Lysette is an American actress. She is well known for appearing on the Amazon Video web television series Transparent. She is a transgender woman and one of the first transgender to appear as a non-transgender person on prime time television in a speaking role.

kfbruin.description: Karen Finney is an MSNBC Political Analyst, a chief democratic strategist, and a columnist for The Hill. She works with political and corporate clients in the USA as well as globally in the sectors of political and communication strategy.

ryan.haddon.description: Ryan Haddon is a prominent American journalist and television producer. She made many appearances by working at MacNeil/Lehrer NewsHour. From her profession, she has made an enormous amount of net worth.

soledadobrien.description: María de la Soledad Teresa O’Brien is an American broadcast journalist and executive producer. Since 2016, O’Brien has been the host for Matter of Fact with Soledad O’Brien, a nationally syndicated weekly talk show produced by Hearst Television. She is chairwoman of Starfish Media Group, a multiplatform media production company and distributor that she founded in 2013. She is also a member of the Peabody Awards board of directors, which is presented by the University of Georgia’s Henry W. Grady College of Journalism and Mass Communication. O’Brien co-anchored CNN’s American Morning from 2003 to 2007, and was the anchor of CNN’s morning news program Starting Point from 2012 to 2013.In 2013, O’Brien became special correspondent on the Al Jazeera America news program America Tonight, and is also a correspondent on HBO’s Real Sports with Bryant Gumbel.

hilariabaldwin.description: Hilaria Baldwin is an American yoga instructor, entrepreneur, podcaster, and author. She was the co-founder of a chain of New York–based yoga studios called Yoga Vida, and has released an exercise DVD and a wellness-focused book. She married into the Baldwin family upon her wedding to actor Alec Baldwin in June 2012, after which her career opportunities increased and media attention was focused on her. In December 2020, she faced allegations that she faked her Spanish accent and misled people about her nationality.

_mauratierney.description: Maura Tierney is an American film and television actress who is best known for her roles as Lisa Miller on the sitcom, NewsRadio, and as Abby Lockhart on the medical drama, ER. Moreover, she also played the role of Helen Solloway on the television drama, The Affair for which she got a Golden Globe Award for Best Supporting Actress – Series, Miniseries or Television Film in 2016.

realmissnatalienunn.description: Natalie Tynika Nunn is an American reality television personality, known for being a castmate on the fourth season of the Bad Girls Club in 2009-10. She subsequently appeared on Bad Girls Club season 13 as well as Hair Battle Spectacular. She was also a contestant on the second season of Love Games: Bad Girls Need Love Too. Nunn also participated on the first season of Bad Girls All-Star Battle. In 2018, she participated in the reality show Celebrity Big Brother.

smoregrace.description: Grace Fulton is an American dancer as well as an aspiring actress who is best known for playing a TV series, Ghost Whisperer as Young Melinda Gordon. Recently, she got more famed after appearing in the famous horror movie, Annabelle: Creation as Grace Fulton. From her profession, she has made a considerable amount of net worth.

patharveynews.description: Pat Harvey is an American broadcast journalist who started co-anchoring for KCAL sister station KCBS news at 5 & 11 PM. She also worked for Walt Disney, owned and operated by KCAL9 in Los Angeles. Further, she is one of the longest-running anchors in Los Angeles.

katemara.description: An actress who rose to prominence for playing Zoe Barnes on the Netflix series House of Cards, Kate Mara is doing really well in the entertainment industry. In the movies Fantastic Four, Brokeback Mountain, Shooter, The Open Road, Transcendence, and The Martian, she has played prominent roles.

piamia.description: Pia Mia Perez is an American singer and actress. She began her career by posting videos of herself singing on the video sharing site YouTube, and went on to star in commercials and music videos. Pia Mia signed a recording contract with Interscope Records in 2013, subsequently releasing her debut extended play, The Gift, and a series of singles, including “Do It Again” and “Touch”. In 2016, she was featured on will.i.am’s single “Boys & Girls” which reached the top 40 in the UK Singles Chart. In 2017, Pia Mia independently released an EP entitled The Gift 2. Pia would later leave Interscope Records and become an independent artist in late 2017, creating her own label Cherry Pie Records. Pia briefly signed a record deal with Republic Records and Electric Feel Entertainment in 2020, before separating the following year.

kaypanabaker.description: Kay Panabaker is an American zoologist as well an actress, best known for her roles as Jenny Garrison in the 2009 reboot Fame and Nikki Westerly on Summerland. Besides her career, many people are curious to know Kay’s personal life.

meadow.williams.description: Meadow Williams is an American actress and producer. In 2000s, Williams began working as film producer, her credits include The Harvest (2013), Den of Thieves (2018) and After (2019).

sibilatv.description: Sibila Vargas is a prominent American news anchor. She is well known for her job as an anchor in WNBC-TV at 5, 6 and 11 p.m. Also, has worked as a producer, and correspondent at CNN as well. From her profession, she has made an impressive amount of net worth.

issarae.description: Issa Rae is an American actress, writer, producer as well as web series creator. She gained fame from her work on the YouTube web series Awkward Black Girl. She also gained recognition for creating, co-writing and starring in the HBO TV series Insecure. For her work on Insecure, she gained two Golden Globe Award nomination for Best Actress TV series Musical.

joannefox5.description: The Emmy award winner, Joanne Feldman is an AMS Certified Broadcast Meteorologist who works at the Fox network’s FOX 5 Storm Team. She is working with the network since 2007.

alydiaz.description: Alyssa Diaz is an American actress who is known for her role as Celia Ortega on the CBS daytime soap opera, As the World Turns. Moreover, she has made her appearance in many other series, The Nine Lives of Chloe King, Army Wives, Ray Donovan, Zoo, and The Rookie.

jujuchangabc.description: Hyunju “Juju” Chang is an American television journalist for ABC News, and currently serves as an anchor of Nightline. She previously served as a special correspondent and fill-in anchor for Nightline, and was also the news anchor for ABC News’ morning news program Good Morning America from 2009–2011.

andreanavedo.description: Andrea Navedo is an American actress who is famous for her appearance on the daytime soap operas, One Life to Live (1995–1997) and Guiding Light (1999-2000), and in several supporting roles on primetime television. meganomullally.description: Megan Mullally is an American actress, comedian, and singer who is best known for her starring role as Karen Walker on the NBC sitcom, Will & Grace (1998–2006, 2017–present). Moreover, she received 8th Primetime Emmy Award nominations for Outstanding Supporting Actress in a Comedy Series winning twice in 2000 and 2006.

kikilayne.description: Kiandra “KiKi” Layne is an American actress. elsabaldaiaa.description: Elsa Baldaia is a New York based model, born in Angola, Africa. She is a Portuguese national with Angolan, Portuguese & Namibian ethnicity. In 2011, she was a finalist in the International Elite Model Look Contest and won. This encouraged her more and she participated in the Elite Model Look International Contest in Shanghai, China. She was in the top 15 finalists. He favorite thing about modeling is that she gets to travel to different places for work. During her modeling career, she has traveled to various places including Germany, China, Paris, Spain, US, and South Africa. During her career, she has represented many designers and worked with many brands, magazines, and photographers. Still, she has a long way to go. In 2018, she walked the runway for Fall/ Winter 18 Shows for Pamella Roland, Custo Barcelona, Bibhu Mohapatra, Vivienne Tam, Tibi, and Rosie Assoulin. In the Spring/ Summer 2018, she appeared in the Levi’s Accessories Campaign. In August 2018, Elsa was featured in an editorial for Paper Magazine. For this project, she worked with Stefano Ortega. This editorial was named Missed Moment. In 2019, she walked the Fall/ Winter 19 Show for Ozwald Boateng, Sherri Hill, and Veronica Beard. Later, she walked for John Richmond Spring/ Summer 20 Men’s Show. The best place she visited was Paris. She lived in the city for 3 months and it was an unforgettable trip. Though she couldn’t speak French, she did not lose hope. When it was her first day, she went to the agency and all she said was “yes”. At first, she didn’t believe herself as she was alone in a new city. This was not easy for her, but it was a rewarding experience. She was rejected plenty of times, yet, she remained strong. Recently, she is living in New York. Elsa Baldaia is an Angolan model who has the skills, talent, and beauty of becoming a top model.

Rubina’s style is versatile yet she tends to work with abstract expressionism and portraiture the most. She also expresses her creativity in other media and formats like film photography and even embroidery.

In 2013 Sodre’s Mother agency, Elo Management (São Paulo, Brazil), changed her to Major Models New York what sparkled a lawsuit from Marilyn NY who claimed that Sodre had broken her contract with them. She has appeared in editorials for Marie Claire Brazil, US Cosmopolitan, L’Officiel Switzerland, L’Officiel Brasil (including cover), Elle South Africa, Glamour South Africa, Nylon Magazine and Wonderland Magazine to name some. She spent three weeks inside the house. She also appeared on the reality dance show ‘Jhalak Dikhhla Jaa,’ which was on the lines of ‘Dancing with the Stars.’ She dated Indian actor Angad Bedi for a while but ended the relationship when he chose to marry Neha Dhupia. rieledowns.description: Riele Downs is a Canadian child actress who is famous for her role as Charlotte on the Nickelodeon television series, Henry Danger. Additionally, she is also known for her role as Faith Sullivan in the 2013 film, The Best man Holiday.

laurenorlando88.description: Lauren Orlando is a fifteen-year-old social media influencer who shares her youthful, bubbly personality and love for creativity with an accumulated digital audience of over nine million followers. Born in Toronto, Ontario, Lauren now splits her time between her hometown and Los Angeles, California. On her YouTube channel, Lauren posts fashion, beauty and lifestyle content, as well as challenges that often feature her friends and her brother, Johnny. Lauren is also passionate about acting. She stars as Kate in Brat’s hit digital series Total Eclipse (2018). Lauren is also thrilled to feature in Next Level (2019), which is her first film role. She aspires to work on more television and movie projects in the future. In her spare time, Lauren enjoys hanging out with her family, watching Netflix and playing with her dogs, Bentley and Leo.

jodellemicah.description: Jodelle Ferland, born as Jodelle Micah Ferland is a famous Canadian actress best known for her roles in the 2004 ABC television series Kingdom Hospital as Mary Jensen. Apart from it, she has played on The Twilight Saga: Eclipse as Bree Tanner.

lennonstella.description: Lennon Ray Louise Stella is a Canadian singer and actress. She portrayed Maddie Conrad on the musical-drama series Nashville (2012–18). Before going solo in 2018, Stella performed with her sister as the duo Lennon & Maisy. Stella released her debut EP Love, Me in 2018. Her debut studio album Three. Two. One. was released on April 24, 2020.

katetoddlifestyle.description: Kate Todd is a Canadian actress and singer-songwriter. She is best known for her roles as Lily Randall in Radio Free Roscoe and Sally in Life with Derek. She is also known for her continuing role as Erica in the movie and series My Babysitter’s a Vampire and has a recurring role in the Canadian drama series The L.A. Complex as Katee.

realmisacampo.description: Misa Campo is a Canadian import model and social media star currently based in Los Angeles, California. Starting out as a sports car model, she took part in Montreal Sport Compact Performance Auto Show in 2006. The same year, she won the Miss Rocawear Canada beauty pageant. In September 2006, she was featured on the ‘Maxim’ magazine as one of their “Show Us Something” girls. Since then, she started to appear regularly on a number of magazines including ‘Super Street’, ‘Version C Models Magazine’, ‘Uno’, and ‘DragSport’ magazines. She was named Model of the Month for the December 2006 issue of the DragSport magazine. In 2007, she was named IGN DVD Babe of the Day. In 2011, she appeared as a main cast in the Indonesian horror movie ‘Pacar Hantu Perawan’. She was named one of the FHM 100 Sexiest Women in 2011 and was the cover girl of FHM magazine in February 2011. In May 2013, she did a photoshoot for SSUR Lookbook Summer 2013, working with one of her favorite photographers, Van Styles. While she is known as one of the most famous car shows models, she also supports charitable causes and took part in Team District 10’s 8th Annual Breast Cancer Awareness Fundraiser Car Show in October 2014. Misa Campo started her career as a bartender, working at the exclusive Jet and System Night Club in Montreal. During this time, she was offered modeling jobs after being spotted by her boss, who encouraged her to try her luck at modeling. She initially modeled for Montreal’s annual racing car show Sport Compact Performance, one of the biggest sports car shows in Canada. However, in 2006, she started to compete on beauty pageants and eventually became Miss Rocawear Canada 2006. She then moved to California to further her modeling career and became a bartender at a club in Los Angeles, while still looking for modeling opportunities. Her modeling career skyrocketed after she posed for a number of prestigious magazines like Maxim and DragSport. After her initial success as a model, Misa Campo, in 2008, decided to move to Japan with the ambition of becoming a singing star. While her entry into the Japanese music industry was not announced by any prominent record label, she herself announced through her personal blog that she has signed a record deal with a Japanese record label. The next year, she moved to Japan for an initial 6-month stay to consolidate her new career. She was touted as a replacement for another import model of Filipino descent, named Leah Dizon, who moved from America to Japan in 2006 to become a singer. After Dizon decided to take a break, her fans started to think of Campo as an alternative. While she was part Asian by birth (Filipino), she didn’t know Japanese at all, but hoped to learn the language during her stay like her predecessor Dizon. However, she eventually moved back to Canada as her new career didn’t make much of an impression. Misa Campo soon started her social media journey by creating accounts on various social media platforms like Twitter, Instagram and later YouTube. She is particularly known for the risqué pictures she shares on her Instagram profile, which helped her in increasing her popularity on social media manifold. She has already modeled for many magazines and has been featured on many entertainment websites; but she would like to be a Sports Illustrated swimsuit model in the future.

Toubia garnered significant fame in 2008 when she took part the second season of the Univision beauty pageant series ‘Nuestra Belleza Latina’. She made her acting debut in 2010, portraying a receptionist in an episode of Telemundo’s telenovela ‘Aurora’. In 2015, she appeared in her first and only film to date, the action-drama ‘Tattooed Love’. Also known as the ‘Fairy Sister’, Yifei has acted in series ‘The Story of a Noble Family’, ‘Demi-Gods and Semi-Devils’, ‘Chinese Paladin’ and ‘The Return of the Condor Heroes’. Besides these, she has appeared in several movies including ‘A Chinese Fairy Tale’, ‘The Assassins’, ‘The Forbidden Kingdom’, ‘Once Upon a Time’, ‘Hanson and the Beast’, ‘The Third Way of Love’, ‘So Young 2: Never Gone’ and ‘The Chinese Widow’, to name a few. The sweet-looking actress is also a singer who has released the albums ‘Liu Yifei’, ‘All My Words’, ‘Mayonaka no door’ as well as recorded several soundtracks for various artists. Talking about her honours and awards, Yifei received the ‘Most Charismatic Actress’ award at the 22nd Hong Kong Society of Cinematographers Award ceremony. She also received the ‘Best Actress’ award at 5th Macau International Movie Festival for her work in ‘The Assassins.’ In addition to these, the Chinese star was awarded the ‘Most Popular Actress’ award at the 13th Guangzhou College Student Film Festival. She also fetched the ‘Most Anticipated Actress’ award at the 16th Chinese Film Media Awards for her project, ‘The Third Way of Love.’

In 2017, Liu became the second Chinese model to ever appear on the cover of American Vogue, and the first to be featured on the front cover rather than foldout. She landed on the cover a second time in American Vogue’s April 2020 issue, becoming the first person of Chinese descent to appear twice. faye_fa_ye.description: Faye Wong is a Chinese-born Hong Kong singer-songwriter and actress, often referred as the “Diva of Asia”. Early in her career she briefly used the stage name Shirley Wong. Born in Beijing, she moved to British Hong Kong in 1987 and came to public attention in the early 1990s by singing in Cantonese, often combining alternative music with mainstream Chinese pop. Since 1994 she has recorded mostly in her native Mandarin. In 2000 she was recognised by Guinness World Records as the Best Selling Canto-Pop Female. Following her second marriage in 2005 she withdrew from the limelight, but returned to the stage in 2010. Popular in Mainland China, Taiwan, Hong Kong and Singapore, she has also gained a large following in Japan. In the West she is perhaps best known for starring in Wong Kar-wai’s films Chungking Express and 2046. While she has collaborated with international artists such as Cocteau Twins, Wong recorded only a few songs in English, including “Eyes on Me”—the theme song of the video game Final Fantasy VIII. Wong is known to be a “diva with few words” in public, and has gained a reputation for her “cool” personality. In Encyclopedia of Contemporary Chinese Culture, Jeroen de Kloet characterised her as “singer, actress, mother, celebrity, royalty, sex symbol and diva all at the same time”. Wong is considered by some as one of East Asia’s biggest popstars with a career of over 30 years.

But somehow, Pia found a way into the Filipino entertainment industry and started earning bread and butter for her family. lilyrose_depp.description: Lily-Rose Melody Depp is a French-American actress and model. A year later, she campaigned for the brand’s fragrance Chanel No.5 L’Eau, which saw a 30 percent boost in sales, making her a popular teenage model in the industry. She was also cast in Chanel’s Rouge Coco Gloss campaign, and its Autumn/Winter 2017 campaign, making her the youngest Chanel brand ambassador till date. The daughter of American actor Johnny Depp and French singer and actress Vanessa Paradis, she has always been in the media limelight. In fact, she attracted huge media attention when she attended Chanel’s Métiers d’Art Collection show in New York with her mother, and became popular overnight. As a model, she has been featured in both the British and the French editions of ‘Vogue.’ Besides modeling, she has also embarked on an acting career and debuted in the Canadian comedy-horror film ‘Tusk’, which premiered at the Toronto International Film Festival in 2014. She has appeared in the movies ‘Yoga Hosers’, ‘La Danseuse’, and ‘Planetarium’ as well. She is also a social media personality, with 4.1 million followers on Instagram.

manonleloup.description: Manon Leloup, born in Northern France, was spotted in her hometown at the age of 15. At first skeptical about starting a modeling career, she took on theatrical classes while still in school. Two years later, however, Manon changed her mind and decided to give modeling a try. She received her break courtesy of Calvin Klein when she walked in the brand’s SS 2013 show as well as over 50 additional shows the same season including Prada, Céline, Dior, Valentino, Marc Jacobs, Stella Mccartney, and Jean Paul Gaultier for whom she has not missed a show ever since. Manon has been featured in American and Italian Vogue, Love magazine and Self Service to name only a few. She has been photographed by Inez & Vinoodh, Annie Leibovitz, Lachlan Bailey, Venetia Scott, Greg Kadel, Emma Summerton, Daniel Jackson and David Sims for who she was editorially exclusive for six months. She has also served as the face of several fashion campaigns including Balmain, Sportmax, Carolina Herrera and Louis Vuitton. Over the years working as a model, the brunette beauty has developed a keen sense of style as well as a sharp eye for photography which has naturally led to success as a photographer herself.

pom.klementieff.description: Pom Klementieff is an actress from France who has gained international fame for portraying the role of Mantis in the Marvel Cinematic Universe films. She has also delivered memorable performances in films like ‘Loup’, ‘Sleepless Night’, and ‘Oldboy’. Klementieff was born when her parents were living in Quebec City, Canada. She spent the first year of her life in Canada and then relocated to Japan and then to the Ivory Coast with her family. Eventually, they settled in France. When she was 19 years old, she decided to pursue a career as an actress and enrolled at the Cours Florent drama school in Paris. Klementieff made her acting debut in the 2007 French independent film ‘Après lui’, in which she worked opposite Catherine Deneuve. Her television debut came about a couple of years later, in the miniseries ‘Pigalle, la nuit’. In 2013, she appeared in her first Hollywood film, Spike Lee’s ‘Oldboy’. After two years, Klementieff joined the MCU, and her first film in the franchise, ‘Guardians of the Galaxy Vol. 2’, was released. She has since appeared in two more films in the franchise, ‘Avengers: Infinity War’ and ‘Avengers: Endgame’.
