She is known for her Beautiful Looks, cute smile, Modeling Poses, Style, and Amazing Personality. She is among one of the most trending girls on Instagram. Her social media presence is growing at an astounding pace She is also popular for her eye-catching Instagram pictures and Videos.

pamela_rf.description: Pamela Reif is a German-born fitness model and social media star. Her rise to success all began at the age of 16, when she started posting pictures of her lifestyle online. People became intrigued by Pamela’s aesthetic and lean physique, so much so, that they started spreading the word about the German model among others. Before long, Pamela’s social media sites started growing like never before, as she slowly made her way to the top of the fitness and social media world. By 2018, Pamela became a worldwide fitness sensation, with an army of followers who support her every step of the way. Fitness model and social media sensation whose gained more than 6.9 million followers on Instagram posting photos and exercise videos.

melaniekroll.description: Melanie Kroll is the famous Model, and Instagram Star from Germany. She has appeared in many Videos. She is known for her Beautiful Looks, cute smile, Modelling Poses, Style, and Amazing Personality. She is among one of the most trending girls on Instagram. Her social media presence is growing at an astounding pace She is also popular for her eye-catching Instagram pictures and Videos. She has a huge fan following.

maren_tschinkel.description: Maren Tschinkel is a German international model and beauty pageant titleholder who was crowned as Miss Earth Germany 2018. She represented Germany in the Miss Earth 2018 international pageant.

katulka_.description: Katulka is best known as a TikTok Star. Crown verified German TikTok representative primarily known for her lip-sync and transition content on the app. Her videos earned her the transition and style guru badge distinction in addition to 1.1 million fans. She was born on October 31, 1999 in Germany. She has collaborated on content with Typisch Kassii. She was a competitive dancer with a group known as dance2beats.

dinadenoire.description: Social media savant who has earned more than 960k followers posting frequent selfies and snippets of her singing to her dinadenoire Instagram account.

juliaroemmelt.description: Julia Roemmelt, a German model and beauty and style influencer from Speyer gained an audience base on her Instagram handle @juliaroemmelt. She posted first on her Instagram account in June 2016. Later she posted many posts with her family. She has added many story highlights on her account about fashion, travel, food, workout, friends and more.

goldenbarbie.description: Model for brands such as Forever21, Smashbox, American Eagle, Seventeen, Glamour, Ralph Lauren and more who is an Instagram sensation with over 4.1 million followers.

janajung.description: Model and social media star who is best known for having earned representation as a model from Elite Model Management. She is best known for sharing a mix of modeling and traveling photos to over 85k Instagram followers.

melindalondon.description: Elite Model represented professional who earned more than 890k followers on Instagram. She is known by the nickname Sharky. She was a teenager when she began her professional modeling career. She has modeled for Playboy.

adriennejueliger.description: Adrienne was born June 6, 1997 in Bonn, Germany. She’s represented by DNA Models in New York and couple of others modeling agencies in European countries. Juliger made her catwalk debut on the Prada fashion show in Milan, Italy at the early age of seventeen. In October 2015, Adrienne won the title Miss Vogue. According to multiple rumors, her boyfriend is Brooklyn Beckham, son of David and Victoria Beckham. But their relationship was never publicly confirmed.

lena_hardt.description: Anna Lena Hardt started her carrier in 2012 with shows like Yves Saint Laurent, Burberry, Versace, Christopher Kane and Giles. After graduating high school she moved from Cologne to Paris and still calls the city of love her home.

louschoof.description: German-born Lou Schoof has worked as both a fashion model and photographer for publications like American, British, Italian and German Vogue. In 2020, Lou became a leader in the fashion industry after committing to only partnering with brands with a high ethical standard and fair trade business model.

carolaremer.description: Carola Remer is a German model. Remer was born in Hagen, near Düsseldorf in Nordrhine-Westphalia in Germany. Her father is a surgeon and her mother, a pharmacist. She has one younger sister. Remer was planning a career in medicine, completing three semesters, until her cousin sent photos of her to a local modeling agency. Remer had her breakthrough in 2011. She had an immense editorial response gaining work for Japanese Vogue, Chinese Vogue, and Harper’s Bazaar. She booked those projects before making her fall 2011 catwalk debut, where she modeled for Ralph Lauren, Emilio Pucci, Jean Paul Gaultier and Tom Ford. Later she added other firms including Philosophy di Alberta Ferretti, Ruffian, Diane von Furstenberg, Rochas, Ohne Titel, Halston, Cacharel, Hakaan, Gianfranco Ferre, Brioni, Moschino, Rad Hourani, Sportmax and Roland Mouret. She appeared in campaigns for Agent Provocateur and Husky.

juliastegner.description: Julia Stegner is a German model. Stegner, the daughter of Günter Stegner, the Director Central and Eastern Europe for LSI Corporation, and Erika Stegner, an accountant, was raised in an animal-loving household with many dogs alongside her older sister Jeanette, who currently works in film production. For seven years she was a child model, appearing in commercials and children’s catalogs, and for nine years was trained in dance.

lorena.description: Lorena Rae is a German International model and an actress. Also, she is a PMA model. She is mainly known for her walk in the Victoria’s Secret Fashion Show 2018. Lorena also represented an L’oreal at Cannes Film Festival. Also, she performed on the runway for Calzadonia and Shaiatzy Chen. Additionally, Lorena played a role in Fashion Police as well.

tonigarrn.description: Toni Garrn is a Model who got her break into the industry by signing an exclusive contract with Calvin Klein in 2008. She eventually started modeling for Victoria’s Secret in 2011. She was discovered at age 13 by a model scout for Modelwerk, a successful German agency. Unlike most models, she wore a size six, which was considered plus size and heavy.

carolinelossberg.description: Caroline Lossberg is a German model who is best known for her photography campaigns and popular Instagram page. Her Instagram account features lifestyle, beauty, and travel photos. She has been a brand ambassador for Esprit. She has amassed over 100k followers to her Instagram page.

jordan.carver.real.description: Jordan Carver is a glamour model, entrepreneur, and actress of German-Italian origin. Besides that, she is a spokesperson as well as an international figure for the Redcoon. Redcoon is a German electronics company.

barbarameier.description: Among all those famous German actresses and models, Barbara Meier is also one of them. She is most recognized as the winner of the second season of Germany’s Next Topmodel.

cathyhummels.description: German television presenter best known for her coverage of high-profile events like Berlin Fashion Week and the 2014 FIFA World Cup. She gained additional fame as a competitor on the dance competition show Let’s Dance in 2015. She graduated from the Technical University of Dortmund.

laraoff1_.description: To have a successful profession as an actor, YouTuber, and singer at a young age, isn’t easy; but when you have a talent as well as a passion to make it happen, you can achieve anything in life. Teen sensation Its Lara is the perfect example. The 16-year-old YouTube star, Lara has more than 146K followers on her YouTube channel as of November 2018. Read the full article to know about her earning, boyfriend and many more.

vismaramartina.description: Instagram model and social media influencer who rose to fame by sharing fashion, swimwear, and travel photos on her vismaramartina account. She has partnered with several fashion and athletic wear brands including WALL and Thèoria Milano. She has over 3.2 million followers on Instagram. Her Youtube channel has accumulated close to 100k subscribers.

vanessaaxente.description: Known for her work in New York, Paris, and Milan, this Hungarian-born model appeared in runway shows for such renowned fashion labels as Prada, Christian Dior, Louis Vuitton, Donna Karan, and Calvin Klein. After signing in 2009 with the Budapest-based Attractive Models agency and subsequently transferring to VIVA Model Management, followed by DNA Model Management, she made her Western European runway debut in a 2012 Prada showcase in Milan, Italy. She appeared on the covers of the German and Japanese versions of Vogue in 2013 and 2014, respectively.

eniko.description: Widely recognized as one of the top models from Hungary, Eniko Mihalik began her storied career after winning her country’s Elite Model Look competition. A reputable tour de force in front of the camera, she went on to be a favorite of legendary photographers such as Inez Van Lamsweerde & Vinoodh Matadin, Craig McDean, and Mario Sorrenti, as well as revered stylists such as Carine Roitfeld. She has been the campaign face for numerous luxury brands, such as Gucci, Chloe, MaxMara, Hugo Boss, and Alberta Ferretti, in addition to beauty giants like L’Oreal and Shiseido. She has also landed over 60 magazine covers in her career thus far, including V, i-D, Japanese Vogue, and Harper’s Bazaar. Beyond modeling, Eniko is an avid runner, having completed her first marathon in 2017. She has also been working closely with UNICEF, with her most recent fundraising effort for the organization being a clothing donation drive that gathered lucrative items for resale.

realbarbarapalvin.description: This doe-eyed brunette started off early and soon attracted fame and attention from the who’s who of the fashion industry as a young teenager. Through her style and photogenic-killer looks, Barbara Palvin grabbed eyeballs of major fashion houses. This Budapest-born babe is, indeed, one of the hottest models in the world, who has done catwalk shows for numerous fashion brands and has appeared on various international magazine covers. She was declared as the youngest and newest muse of L’Oreal Paris at the age of 19 years, thus joining the L’Oreal Paris family with celebrities Gwen Stefani and Claudia Schiffer. Through her fascinating personality and great sense of humor, she infused freshness and elegance, thereby being considered a promising supermodel with incredible potential to reach the sky. She became a Victoria’s Secret Angel in 2012, thanks to her sublime beauty and perfect body. In a short span of time, she made a name for herself in the fashion industry and is deemed to be one of the youngest supermodels in recent times. Apart from gaining attention for working as a fashion and lingerie model, this Hungarian stunner was also in the media news for having a rumored brief fling with distinguished pop star, Justin Bieber, and being the reason behind the latter’s split with Selena Gomez.

dishapatani.description: Disha Patani is a famous Indian model and aBollywood actress. Before marking her debut with a Telugu film ‘Loafer'(2015), she was already a famous face in the modeling world. Patani is best known for her portrayal of the role of ‘Priyanka Jha’ in the Bollywood move “M.S. Dhoni: The Untold Story”. After completing her schooling, Disha went to Amity University, Lucknow to pursue a degree in Computer Scince and Engineering. While she was atill in the first year, she started receiving a number of modelling offers. She dropped out of the second year of her degree and went on to articipate in the 2013 Femina India Indore. Disha Patani was declared the first runner-up. Surprisingly, she also auditioned for the film ‘ Heropanti’ but got rejected.

imouniroy.description: Mouni Roy is an Indian actress, singer, Kathak dancer and model. She is best Known for her role of “sati” in the TV serial “Devon ke Dev…Mahadev” and “Naagin” in “Nagin 2 – Mohabbat Aur Inteqaam Ki Dastaan.” She became a household name with her portrayal of the role of “krishna Tulsi” in the TV serial “Kyunki Saas Bhi Kabhi The” which was also her debut.

anveshi25.description: Anveshi Jain is an Indian model, actress, host and emcee who has hosted many corporate events, campusevents, religious funtions, charity events, private parties, wedings, etc.

shamasikander.description: Shama Sikander is an Indian actress who is best recognised for her lead roles in TV series like Yeh Meri Life Hai (2003-2005) and groundbreaking web content like the short film Sexaholic and the mini-series Maaya: Slave of Her Desires. On the big screen, Sikander has appeared in numerous Bollywood films, including starting her career with the 1999 Aamir Khan starrer Mann. Her last theatrical release, a Bollywood thriller, Bypass Road was released on 8 November 2019.

urvashirautela.description: Urvashi Rautela is an Indian actress and model who appears in Bollywood films. She was crowned Miss Diva Universe 2015 and represented India at the Miss Universe 2015 pageant. She made her Bollywood debut with Singh Saab the Great (2013) and appeared in films like Sanam Re (2016), Great Grand Masti (2016), Hate Story 4 (2018) and Pagalpanti (2019).

sakshimalikk.description: Sakshi Malik is a Model and Actress from India. She was born and raised in New Delhi and moved later for her career in Mumbai. For a long time, she has worked as a Toabh Model. Sakshi was in love with modeling during college. In fashion events, she used to be participating. She stepped into the glamorous world following graduation in Mumbai. Via advertising, Sakshi began her career. With brands like PC Jewelers, FreshBooks, Adidas she has served. In her Instagram profile, she described herself as an influence of fashion, beauty, and lifestyle. For a long time, she has worked as a model. Throughout her college days, she began her modeling career, attending most of the college events and styles. She has decided that she is modeling her real passion and love.

nehamalik335.description: Neha Malik is an Indian Actress and Model, she has appeared in several hit video songs and Bollywood movies. Neha Malik had done her Medical education in Chandigarh and went to Indore for the Frankfinn course and at last, she came to Mumbai and started pursuing her actress and model career. She finally got her first Serial in 2013 name “Fearless” on UTV Bindass. She debuted in the Bollywood Movie “Bhanwari Ka Jaal”. And her first Music video song was “Ishq Karle” with Mika Singh and Sonu Nigam.

swethaa_naidu.description: Swetha Naidu is an Instagram Star.Swetha Naidu was born in 1 October 1995 in Andhra Pradesh, India India in a middle-class family. She was raised in Andhra Pradesh, India and completed her education from Andhra Pradesh, India. She is 21 years old.She is well known for posting awesome images and short videos on her Instagram account. Swetha Naidu has earned over 497K followers on Instagram. She is popular over different social media platforms and has gained huge popularity.

anishadixit.description: Anisha Dixit is a popular Indian YouTuber who is mainly known for her appearances on the Rikshawali YouTube Channel. Anisha has completed her high school in Germany and has completed a diploma in acting from Switzerland. Currently, she resides in Mumbai, Maharashtra, and runs her YouTube channel where she uploads comedy videos and Vlog. She has more than 3 million subscribers on her YouTube channel. Anisha has a collab with a lot of celebrities on her YouTube videos including Kartik Aryan and Sara Ali Khan. Besides this, she has also appeared in movies and music videos as well.

kat.kristian.description: Kat Kristian is an Indian actress and model. She was born in 1997 in Mumbai, Maharashtra. Recently she has worked in the video song of Tony Kakkar and Neha Kakkar “Goa Beach”. Initially, Kat Kristian gain huge popularity as a contestant of famous indian reality show “India’s Next Top Model” which was aired on MTv. She had got the wild card entry to the show. Kat Kristian has also done many Tv commercials like Brand Factory, Myntra, Jockey etc.

nehasharmaofficial.description: Neha Sharma is an Indian actress and model. A native of Bihar, Sharma attended the Mount Carmel School in Bhagalpur and pursued a course in fashion design from the National Institute of Fashion Technology (NIFT) in New Delhi. Sharma’s first role was in the Telugu film Chirutha, released on September 28, 2007. Her first Hindi film was Crook directed by Mohit Suri, released on October 8, 2010. Sharma made a cameo appearance in the 2012 romantic comedy film Teri Meri Kahaani directed by Kunal Kohli. She was highly appreciated in the semi-hit Kyaa Super Kool Hai Hum.

avneetkaur_13.description: Actress known for her television debut playing Jhilmil in the soap opera Meri Maa. She has since made her film debut in the 2014 movie Mardaani and gained popularity portraying the lead character of Khushi in Hamari Sister Didi. She first rose to fame in 2010 as a finalist in the dance competition series Dance India Dance Li’l Masters. She followed shortly after in the spinoff dance competition series, Dance Ke Superstars. She participated in the 2012 season of Jhalak Dikhhla Jaa, India’s version of the BBC’s Strictly Come Dancing.

aliaabhatt.description: Alia Bhatt is a stylish and attractive Indian movie actress and singer who acts in Bollywood.Alia is also recognized as the daughter of Mahesh Bhatt who is a great filmmaker and Soni Razdan who is also an actress.Alia performed her opening head character in Karan Johar’s romantic drama Student of the Year-2012, which gained her a proposal for the Filmfare Award for Best Female Debut.Alia has given an exceptional act on her performance as an actress in every movie that she has achieved.Alia is experienced actress who holds her life not just to make tremendous money but it is her enthusiasm.Alia has gained a huge admiration and fans throughout her life.

aslisona.description: Sonakshi Sinha is a distinguished Indian actress who is also known as an offspring of legendary actors named Shatrughan and Poonam Sinha. Sinha started her acting appearance in the action-drama movie Dabangg-2010 opposite to Salman Khan, which obtained her all the Debut awards holding the Filmfare Award for Best Female Debut after serving as a costume designer in her old career.

manushi_chhillar.description: Manushi Chhillar is an Indian model and beauty pageant who is crowned with Miss World 2017 Title. Earlier she was crowned with Femina Miss India 2017 on 25 June 2017. Similarly, Chhillar is the sixth Indian woman to conquer Miss World and the beginning since Priyanka Chopra won Miss World-2000. Manushi has furnished an outstanding success on her job as a Model. Moreover, Manushi has great knowledge feature but she focused on her career.

priyankachopra.description: Priyanka Chopra Jonas was born on India, to the family of Capt. Dr. Ashok Chopra and Dr. Madhu Chopra, both Indian Army physicians. She had a very varied upbringing. She started her education at La Martinière Girls College in Lucknow as a resident student; a short stay at Maria Goretti College in Bareilly prepared her for further studies in the U.S. Having completed tenth grade in Boston, Massachusetts, U.S., she decided to become a software engineer or a criminal psychologist. She enjoys Indian music and dance; flair for writing poetry and short stories; reading, especially biographies; and has worked for a lot of social welfare programs.

aalishapanwar157.description: “Acting is behaving truthfully under imaginary circumstances.” And, Alisha Panwar has justice her each and every on-screen character she got to portray so far. No, one on trending, she is well-recognized for her role on Zee TV’s Jamai Raja, and Colors TV’s Thapki Pyar Ki.

shirleysetia.description: An Indo-Kiwi singer, Shirley Setia is not only a popular singer on YouTube but also a Radio Tarana RJ of the show Showtime with Shirley. To the date, she has collaborated with YouTube stars across Canada, India, and U.K.

aabhabakaya.description: Widely known for her innovative leadership quality with the ability to think outside the box, Aabha Bakaya is the founder of AB Network Pvt Ltd. She started her career in 2002 as a correspondent in Business Today Magazine. Previously, Aabha worked in several networks like CNBC TV18, NDTV PROFIT, and NDTV GOOD TIMES.

mandirabedi.description: Mandira Bedi is an Indian actress, model, fashion designer and also, a television presenter. Mandira has worked in a number of Indian serials as well as movies. Also, Mandira has gained a lot of popularity through her exceptional talent. Later, she performed the title role in Doordarshan Channel’s daily soap called Shanti in 1994.

laurabas.description: Laura Basuki is an Indonesian model and actress. She won a Citra Award for Best Leading Actress for her role in the 2010 film Tiga Hati, Dua Dunia, Satu Cinta (Three Hearts, Two Worlds, One Love). Her first modelling job was at a bridal pageant showing the works of Bijan Wanaatmadja. This was followed by spots marketing products including Coca-Cola and Vaseline. The weekly entertainment magazine Tabloid Nova, Basuki’s compared her look to that of Japanese porn star Maria Ozawa. As the modelling work kept her too busy to study medicine, Basuki began studying economics. In 2008, Basuki was cast in her first role, Gara-Gara Bola (Because of Football), after the producer Nia Dinata saw Basuki’s face in a magazine. She played the role of a bookie’s wife after a month of coaching. Gara-Gara Bola garnered her two awards at the 2009 Indonesian Movie Awards. Two years later, Basuki played a Catholic woman in love with a Muslim man in Tiga Hati, Dua Dunia, Satu Cinta (Three Hearts, Two Worlds, One Love), which was a critical success. For her work, Basuki received a Citra Award for Best Actress at the 2010 Indonesian Film Festival. Also in 2010, Basuki served as an emcee hosting a quiz show for the MNC Group; the programme, broadcast during the 2010 FIFA World Cup, was about football. Basuki married businessman Leo Sanjaya in 2011. In early 2012, she played a journalist in Agus Kuntz’ film Republik Twitter (The Twitter Republic). Basuki’s fourth film, Di Timur Matahari (East of the Sun), debuted on 12 June 2012. A children’s movie directed by Ari Sihasale, it followed Basuki’s character Vina as she moved to Papua with her Papuan husband. For the shooting, she spent over a month in the mountainous inner regions of the island, bathing only weekly. In 2013 she was in a film entitled Madre. In 2015 she was in the film Love and Faith.

putriwithlove.description: What does it take to be a model? Is it a good height, slim body, and beautiful face? Or is it the confidence? Well, Putri Cinta is that wonderful model who is body confident and does not hesitate to go nude, semi-nude during her photoshoot. She loves her work and does her best to thrive in the fashion industry. There are a lot of things that you might be missing about this hot model. But in this article, we will do our best to fill in those information gaps. Along with her age, height, body, career, the net worth, we will unravel everything about Putri Cinta. Let’s take a look at some quick facts.

rianariani.description: Illusionist and magician, The Sacred Riana came to limelight with her appearance on the reality show Asia’s Got Talent. Her ghostly and horrific act became the highlight of the show in 2017. No wonder, she got many accolades for her work and went on to win the competition.

neginvaand.description: Persian beauty and fashion enthusiast popular as a lifestyle influencer on Instagram, with more than 750,000 followers under the username of neginvaand.

sophia_mitch.description: Sophia Mitchell is an upcoming Irish model, dancer, YouTuber and Instagram star. She is better known as a sponsored model of the famous modelling agency ‘Models 1 London’ who discovered her at an early age. She rose to fame from her activities on her YouTube channel, where she has a huge fan following. She has built up a reputation to be a very talented and multifaceted model, matured much ahead of her age. In fact, there has been a lot of debate online whether a girl, who is just 14 years old, should be exposed on social media the way Sophia was, two years ago when she appeared provocatively dressed on Instagram and Facebook. She has proved to the world that age is no criteria for working on the internet and she has established herself as a model and a star to reckon with. She aspires to have her own brand and franchise and maybe one day get into acting on the big screen. Sophia has the talent and the potential to make it big and we can be sure to see a lot more of her in show business and social media in the days to come.

stellamaxwell.description: Stella Maxwell is a Famous for her participation in the 2014 Victoria’s Secret Fashion Show, this Belgian-Irish model is also known for her advertising campaigns for H&M, Urban Outfitters, Puma, and Ermanno Scervino, as well as for her photo shoots for Glamour, Elle, and Vogue. She began her modeling career while she was a student at the University of Otago in Dunedin, New Zealand. At different points in her career, she was represented by Oui Management, The Lions Agency, and the Why Not Model Agency.

maurahiggins.description: Reality television star best known for her work as a participant on the popular series Love Island. She is also known for her work as a model and ring girl and shares her modeling work and photos through Instagram where she has over 3.1 million followers.

aisling.franciosi.description: Aisling Franciosi is an Irish-Italian actress, who is known for her role of Katie Benedetto in the crime drama TV series ‘The Fall’. The series aired for three seasons between 2013 and 2016, and won several awards and nominations. She is also known for her role in the TV series ‘Legends’, where she played the role of Kate Crawford. It aired in 2014 and 2015 for two seasons. She also appeared in two episodes of ‘Game of Thrones’, the popular fantasy series. She played the role of Lyanna Stark, younger and only sister of Eddard Stark, one of the major characters of the series. In 2018, she was seen in the period drama ‘The Nightingale’, where she played the lead role. For her role in ‘The Nightingale’, she won the AACTA Award in the ‘Best Leading Actress’, category.

olwencatherinekelly.description: There are so many actors and actresses who rose to fame from their acting in movies and TV series. But in today’s case, it’s different; as the actress rose to fame after playing the dead body role with no lines and unfortunately no clothes.

kashymcgrath.description: Katie McGrath is an Irish actress. In television, best recognized for portraying Morgana on the BBC One series Merlin (2008–2012), Lucy Westenra on the British-American series Dracula (2013–2014). Also, as Sarah Bennett in the first season of the Canadian horror anthology series Slasher (2016). And also, for her role as Lena Luthor on the American superhero series Supergirl (2016–present).

littleirishcat.description: Have you had the time to watch the movie Divergent? If not we must say you are missing out a very popular movie of all the time. The movie Divergent is based on a novel written by Veronica Roth. If you have already read the book then you must be wondering who is the stylist behind the curtain of such a huge movie. If you are curious and want to know about him/her then we must say you stumbled upon a correct page. Today we are going to talk about one of the outstanding stylists as well as an actress of all time. She is none other than Cathriona White.

caitrionabalfe.description: Caitríona Balfe is an Irish actress and former model. She is well known for her role as Claire Fraser in the Starz drama series Outlander, for which she has won two People’s Choice Awards, two Saturn Awards, an Irish Film award, and a Television Award. She also received four Golden Globe Award nominations for Best Actress – Television Series Drama.

voguewilliams.description: Vogue Williams is an Irish model, radio and television personality, well known for Fade Street (2010), Bear Grylls: Mission Survive (2015) and Getaways (2017). She has also appeared in Dancing with the Stars and Stepping Out.

ruthkearney.description: Actress best known for starring as Daisy in the Fox drama series The Following. She previously starred as Jess Parker in seasons 4 and 5 of Primeval. In 2016, she began appearing in the Netflix original series Flaked as London. She has guest-starred on the television series Tyrant, Covert Affairs and Holby City.

ruthbradley24.description: Ruth Bradley is an Irish actress known for her role as Emily Merchant in Primeval (2011) and Karen Voss in Humans (2015 to 2018). However, Ruth grabbed the attention of people for playing the role of Antoinette Keegan in Stardust.

hollyhamiltontv.description: The famous lady of the United States, Eleanor Roosevelt once said: The future belongs to those who believe in the beauty of their dreams. Well, this proverb perfectly fit one of the Irish Journalist who works in BBC as an anchor on the Victoria Derbyshire on BBC Two, the BBC News channel, and also BBC Breakfast on BBC One. She is none other than Holly Hamilton.

antonia.campbell.hughes.description: Antonia Campbell-Hughes is a Northern Irish actress and former fashion designer, best known for appearing in Jack Dee’s sitcom Lead Balloon and for portraying Natascha Kampusch in 3096 Days. After the success of series one of Lead Balloon, Campbell-Hughes went on to be cast in a variety of comedy shows on British television, alongside Jennifer Saunders and Alex Macqueen, and went on to create her own one-woman show Bluebell Welch for MTV.

michellefairleys.description: Michelle Fairley is an actress from Northern Ireland, best known for playing Catelyn Stark in the HBO series Game of Thrones (2011–2013), as well as her roles in USA Network series Suits (2013), and Fox series 24: Live Another Day (2014).

yael1c.description: Yael Cohen Aris is a fashion model, software engineer, and Social Influencer. Yael is well-known for her beautiful stunning pictures and videos on social media. Yael is listed as one of the emerging fashion models of Instagram. She has a huge following of “Yael lovers” on social media. On Instagram, she has more than 1m followers.

avital.description: Avital Cohen is a fitness model and social media star hailing from Israel. She’s become one of the fastest growing female fitness stars on the internet, thanks to her awesome workout pictures and videos. Before reaching fame, Avital was someone who enjoyed leading an active and healthy lifestyle. When she turned 18, Avital took the opportunity to enroll in the Israeli Army where she served in the air force. After her service was over, Avital decided to return to her ‘roots’ – focusing on physical exercise and a healthy lifestyle. This time, however, she shared her journey with the online world, posting pictures and videos of her lifestyle. This was a decision Avital has never looked back from. Throughout the years, she’s grown into a social media icon and fitness celebrity with fans from all around the globe.

barrefaeli.description: Bar Refaeli is an Israeli model, television host, and entrepreneur. She is considered among the most internationally successful models to come from Israel, appearing on the cover of the 2009 Sports Illustrated Swimsuit Issue, and being voted No. 1 on Maxim magazine’s Hot 100 list of 2012. As a result, her performance as the superhero, which is the first time for the character on film, was hailed as one of the best parts of the otherwise poorly-received film. The film is part of the DC Extended Universe, and Gadot plays the role again in the solo film Wonder Woman (2017), which was received very positively, and superhero team-up Justice League (2017). Soon enough, the word spread, and her business grew popular. With the release of her first book ‘The Life-Changing Magic of Tidying Up: The Japanese Art of Decluttering and Organizing’, she became a national celebrity in Japan. The book’s translation to English attracted more people, and her fanbase grew. Soon, her book topped the New York Times bestseller list and people started adopting the KonMari method in their everyday lives. She was subsequently named among the 100 most influential people in 2015 by TIME magazine. She gained popularity for her debut role as Lola Valente in the Mexican musical telenovela Lola, érase una vez (2007–2008) and later starred in the lead role of Clara Molina on the Nickelodeon teen drama Sueña conmigo (2010–2011). She gained further success starring as Santanico Pandemonium in the American horror series From Dusk till Dawn: The Series (2014–2016). She is also known for her roles as Monica “Darling” Castello in the action crime film Baby Driver (2017), Nyssiana in the cyberpunk action film Alita: Battle Angel (2019), Madam M in The Fast and the Furious spin-off film Hobbs & Shaw (2019), Fran in the comedy thriller I Care a Lot (2020), and Maia Simmons in the Monsterverse’s film Godzilla vs. Kong (2021).

anapaulasaenzoficialgm.description: na Paula Saenz is a Social media star who is famous for her anapaulasaenzoficialgm Instagram account. ivana.santacruz.description: Ivana Santacruz is a Germany-based Instagram star whose dance, fitness and fashion-related posts have earned her a following of over 1.6 million users on the photo-sharing platform. She is best known for making her fitness regimes fun by incorporating dance routines into them. To inspire others to do the same, the Mexican-origin social media influencer recently launched her own dance and fitness program titled ‘Sweat & Dance’, which offers three 20-minute special dance sessions per week. She is also a YouTuber with almost 175k subscribers on her channel. She signed a sponsorship deal with the international sports brand, PUMA, and often showcases their products on her feed. Santacruz has her own clothing merchandise available for sale via the NA-KD online fashion store. In late 2016, she was chosen as the German face for the promo tour of ‘Keeping up with the Kardashians’, a popular reality television show. She attended the ‘World Fitness Day’ event in Frankfurt in 2018. Ivana Santacruz was an athletic child who trained in gymnastics, but an injury forced her to abandon her professional sports ambitions. It is her love for music that encouraged her to begin dancing when she was 14. She became interested in fitness when she visited a McFIT gym at the age of 16. While the first experience at the gym was quite exhausting for her, she continued her fitness journey, often combining it with dance moves. She began to randomly post her own blend of fitness and dance videos on Instagram in 2014, and her first video was performing a set to the tunes of ‘One Drop’ by QQ. Her videos attracted an increasing number of fans, which made it all the more fun for her. By the end of 2016, she had amassed nearly 700k followers on Instagram and decided to focus more on her YouTube channel. She joined YouTube back in September 2014, but her first video was only uploaded in early 2016. She became more regular on YouTube by the end of 2017 and uploaded dance and workout videos, vlogs, Q&A’s, room tour videos, unboxing, and more on her channel. While her YouTube channel is still picking up, she has made a name for herself as a fitness model on Instagram and launched her own dance and fitness program. While she is well-versed in street-dance, she told NA-KD in December 2018 that she finds modern dance quite inspirational. She also loves classical dance and had once gone to a ballet in New York, even though she could not dance. She did an internship in graphics designing and feels that she would have chosen that profession had she not found fame on Instagram. While she loves to show her creativity on social media platforms, she is also interested in acting on stage, and loves photography as well.

xeniadeli.description: Xenia Deli is a Moldovan-American model. She lives in Los Angeles, California. She has been featured on several fashion magazine covers, including Elle, FMD Magazine and Sport Illustrated of South Africa. She also starred in music videos, including “Thinking About You” and Justin Bieber’s “What Do You Mean?” in 2015. Xenia Deli was born in Basarabia, Moldova. She is ethnically Gagauz. She began studying literature and planned on becoming a teacher, but graduated from the first course of the Moldova State University. She also attended modeling school. She went on an exchange program to the United States from Moldova and worked as a waitress. During her time as a waitress she met her first husband, American photographer Patrick Cox, and through their marriage she gained American citizenship It is unclear when the marriage ended. Later, she attended a program for modeling students, Deli competed in a ‘Beach Bunny’ contest and was one of three finalists. The brand invited her to represent them in their advertising campaign. Soon after that, Deli met photographer Gavin O’Neill, who invited her to shoot. His submission of her photos to a modeling agency resulted in an interview and a contract. In 2010 she moved to South Carolina. Now she divides her time between New York City and Los Angeles. On 4 June 2016 Deli married to then 62-year-old Egyptian (of Palestinian origin) millionaire Ossama Fathi Rabah Al-Sharif, on the island Santorini, in Greece. Her husband has three children of approximately the same age as Deli. Deli started her career with photographs taken by Gavin O’Neill, a fashion photographer, who showed his work to an agency. She got a contract as a model. Deli signed to Elite Model Management in Miami in 2011 and New York City in 2014. Deli picked up a modeling contract with Victoria’s Secret after its representatives saw a poster with her picture from another campaign at a store across from their offices. They invited her for an interview and the parties reached a contract. Deli has been featured on numerous magazine covers, such as Playboy, Love FMD Magazine, Elle Romania, and Sport Illustrated of South Africa. She has also been featured in magazines, including FHM, GQ, Sports Illustrated, Vogue, Harper’s Bazaar, and Maxim. In 2012 Deli appeared nude in Lovecat Magazine. Deli has starred in music videos, including “Wake Me Up” of Ionel Istrati and “Thinking About You” of Calvin Harris. In 2015 Deli co-starred in Justin Bieber’s video “What Do You Mean?,” gaining widespread press attention because of the singer’s popularity, after the video was released on August 28, 2015. This was Bieber’s first No. 1 hit, according to New York Magazine. After the release of the video, Deli said, Bieber’s fans were not happy to see her with their idol. There was widespread speculation about whether she was dating the singing star. Deli played a minor role in The Mindy Project. She has said that she likes to watch movies and she loves acting. She is taking acting classes, and her future plans include to play in movies.

In 2015, she was cast as Ilsa Faust in the American action spy film ‘Mission: Impossible – Rogue Nation’. This made her a popular face on the international level. In 2016, Ferguson bagged important roles in the British Cold War movie ‘Despite the Falling Snow’ and in the biographical drama film ‘Florence Foster Jenkins’. She also did the mystery thriller ‘The Girl on the Train’ the same year. She next played Miranda North in the horror flick ‘Life’ in 2017.
